        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Apply to receive one month free* Offer only eligible up to 48-hours after touring! Towns at Andrew's Park 5925 Allentown Andres Dr. , Suitland, MD, 20746 Call Now - show contact info x 222 OR Text 222 to show contact info to contact our leasing team. Use this link for more information: https://avenue5.aptfeatures.com/s4yy6d Move to a Stunning Camp Springs Rental Community 3 bedroom | 2.5 bath | 2400 square feet Features ✓  Double Vanities ✓  Beautiful Wood Flooring ✓  Private Balconies ✓  New Townhomes ✓  Powder Room ✓  Large Kitchen Islands ✓  Expansive 2400 sqf ✓  Washer and Dryer In-Unit ✓  Granite Countertops ✓  Eat-In Kitchen ✓  A Must See ✓  Top Line Stainless Appliances ✓  High End Finishes ✓  Open Concept Living ✓  Private Two-Car Garage ✓  Walk-In Closets Community Features ✓  Playground ✓  Prime Location Right off I-495 ✓  Tour Today ✓  Bus Stop Located Directly Outside Community ✓  One Mile from Joint Base Andrews ✓  Short Distance to Branch Avenue Metro Station ✓  Onsite Retail: Dominos, Advanced Auto Parts, & Wawa Community Info Newly designed in an incredible location, your new Camp Springs rental home near Andrews Airforce Base lets residents experience a true hidden gem. Enjoy a warm, neighborhood feel in an ideal location right off I-495. Our three and four-bedroom townhomes are thoughtfully appointed with elevated finishes and amenities designed to provide comfort and a sense of home. Pet Policy Pets Allowed Finding a pet friendly apartment can be difficult at times. We know how much you love your furry friends, and we are pleased to welcome four-legged residents to Towns at Andrews Park. We love your pets as much as you do. Please speak with an associate for more details. Office Hours Tuesday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity RjJ9xbihZ",
