        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Limited-Time Move-In Special Receive A Waived Move-In Fee ($500 value!) on Select Apartments.* Tour today or join us for our Open House on Saturday, June 27, from 9 AM–5 PM. *Restrictions may apply. Call the leasing team for all the details. 1328 14th St NW, Washington, DC 20005 Upgrade your DC lifestyle and live life to the fullest in an apartment at The Bentley. Here, the comfort of home and the dynamic vibrance of the city come together to create the perfect living experience. Offering both character and charm, The Bentley has all the fixtures and features you love like high ceilings, oversized windows, and a suite of stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen. Plus, the central location means you have access to everything Logan Circle, Dupont Circle, and the downtown have to offer. This is modern city living. This is home. Apartment Features: City Views in Select Homes High Ceilings with Designer Spot and Track Lighting Open Concept Kitchens with Glossy Italian Cabinetry, Quartz Countertops, Glass Backsplash, and Stainless-Steel Appliances Washer & Dryer Included Wood Toned LVP Flooring Floor-to-Ceiling, Wall-to-Wall Operable Windows Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithborger.com/ew3g2cit/bentley We will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person because the person will provide the rental payment, in whole or in part, through a voucher for rental housing assistance provided by the District or federal government. Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
