        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 13940 Longwood Manor Ct, Woodbridge, VA 22191 If you’re on the hunt for a new apartment in the heart of Woodbridge, look no further than BellaVista. Our spacious 1- and 2- bedroom apartments for rent come with fully equipped kitchens, large walk-in closets, in-unit washers/dryers and more. Select units have been recently renovated and come with private patios and balconies. Our apartments are pet friendly, with access to top-notch amenities including a dog park, vibrant landscaping and ample free parking. The community is also right next door to Lancaster Park which has a playground, volleyball net, basketball courts, grills and more! We have an unbeatable location that our residents love. Woodbridge rests 20 miles south of Washington D.C., nestled in Prince William County, with access to top-rated school districts, public transportation and community parks. It’s a short drive to local shopping attractions like the Potomac Mills and Stonebridge at Potomac Town Center. BellaVista also offers an easy commute via I-95 and Route 1. Everything you need, all right here! Apartment Features: Large Closets Refrigerator Window Coverings Dishwasher Ceiling Fan Air Conditioner Washer/Dryer Newly Renovated Luxury Plank Flooring Patio/Balcony Wooded View Disposal Community Features: On-Site Management On-Site Maintenance Online Payments Bilingual Staff Off Street Parking Bark Park Adjacent to Community Park Reserved Parking Available* Additional Storage Available* Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithrosscompanies.com/usbvuudk/bellavista Managed by ROSS Companies Equal Housing Opportunity Pricing may include current specials and is subject to change without notice.",
