        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Looking to rent out a couple of bedrooms to college students / folks looking for a place to stay. - This includes fully furnished bedrooms, kitchens, and bathrooms. - All utility is included (Verizon Cable, Wifi Internet, Water, Gas, and Heat). - Verizon Fios TV & Internet (50MB/25MB) Commute Access: (Bus Access to GMU, NOVA, & Washington DC) - Transportation access to the Metro Bus (Bus Route 17) is 1 minute in walking distance, which will take you to GMU Fairfax Campus / Vienna Metro Station or Pentagon Metro Station - 5 Minutes from NVCC (Annandale Campus) - 5 Minutes from GMU (Fairfax Campus) - 5 Minutes drive from the beltway Requirements: - Please pay one month up front (deposit) - Monthly rent depending on the term of the lease: Per Room Lease: -$1000 1 Year Lease (Large Room in the Basement) - $900 1Year Lease (Large Room with Private Bathroom & Walk-In Closet) - $850 1 Year Lease (Mid Room with Shared Bathroom) - $800 1 Year Lease (Small Room with Shared Bathroom) *Note: For a month to month lease an additional $100 dollars will be added to the cost. Address: 8600 Thames Street Springfield VA 22151 Contact # show contact info",
