        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 1 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 660 More unit details at: https://Laramar.aptrentnow.com/kr0et0 MODERN STYLE. BREATHTAKING VIEWS. Call Now - show contact info x 194 OR Text 194 to show contact info to chat!   Community Info Experience modern, renovated apartment homes at Bridgeyard Apartments, located in the heart of Old Town Alexandria. Enjoy extraordinary waterfront views of the Potomac River and easy access to I-95/495 for a stress-free commute. Our studio, one, and two-bedroom apartments feature double-paned windows, wood flooring in select units, stylish Lido cabinetry, granite countertops, and energy-efficient appliances, including built-in microwaves. Stay fit with our expansive fitness center and welcome guests with the Butterfly MX smartphone intercom system. Plus, the Mount Vernon Trail is just steps away, offering 18 miles of multi-use recreation trails for walking, running, or biking. Contact us today to schedule a tour! Residence Features ✩  Carpeting ✩  Gas Range ✩  Dishwasher ✩  Microwave ✩  Patio/Balcony ✩  Ceiling Fan ✩  Refrigerator with Icemaker ✩  Hardwood Floors* ✩  Stainless Steel Appliances* ✩  Lido Style Cabinetry ✩  Window Coverings ✩  Air Conditioner ✩  9 Ft Ceilings ✩  Cable Ready ✩  Serene River Views* ✩  Ceramic Kitchen Tile ✩  Chic Two-Panel Interior Doors ✩  Granite Countertops* Community Features ✩  On-Site Maintenance ✩  Beautiful Potomac River Views ✩  Fitness Center ✩  Spanish Speaking Staff ✩  Laundry Facilities ✩  Directly on Mt. Vernon Paved Bike/Hike Trail ✩  Elevator ✩  ButterflyMX Guest Entry Access ✩  Ample Parking Including Garage Options ✩  Sitting area with fire pit ✩  Selected ✩  Waterfront BBQ and Picnic Area ✩  Walk to Old Town Shops and Restaurants ✩  Public Transportation ✩  On-Site Management ✩  Easy Access to Huntington, Eisenhower Ave, and King St. Metro Stations ✩  Fetch Package Delivery Service ✩  Off Street Parking ✩  Swimming Pool right on the Potomac ✩  Courtyard Pet Policy Max 2 Allowed | One time Fee $400 Rent $45 Comments: Maximum 2 pets per home. Certain breed restrictions apply. Restrictions: Pit Bull Terriers, Staffordshire Terriers, Rottweilers, Doberman Pinschers, Chows, Presa Canarios, Akitas, Alaskan Malamutes and Wolf-hybrids. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity o5wHrjD8c9xx",
