        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 3 Baths: 2 Square Feet: 1200 Interested in more information? Visit link below: https://glick.aptdetails.com/lb32y6 Discover your new beginning! Call Now - show contact info x 96 OR Text 96 to show contact info to text our leasing team.   Community Info The Woods of Fairfax Apartments in Lorton, VA is a relaxed community just 15 minutes from the Metro station and 30 minutes from Washington D.C that provides apartment homes in Fairfax, County, VA. This newly renovated community offers one, two, and three bedroom apartment homes with quartz counter tops and plank flooring. Residents enjoy amenities such as a fitness center, bark park, swimming pools with sun decks, grill stations, play parks, and more. Residence Features ✩  New Wood Style Flooring ✩  Full Tub with Ceramic Tile Surround ✩  Cozy, Wood-burning Fireplaces [ 1 ] ✩  1, 2, & 3 Bedroom Apartment Homes ✩  Stylish Finishes ✩  Washer & Dryer ✩  A Must See ✩  New Stainless Appliances ✩  Fully-equipped Kitchen-Including Dishwasher ✩  Completely Renovated Units ✩  Upgrades Everywhere ✩  Scenic Wooded Views [ 1 ] ✩  Abundance of Closet Space 1. Select Units Community Features ✩  Flexible Leases 2 - 15 months ✩  Covered Parking ✩  Tour Today ✩  Fitness on Demand ✩  Lighted Sports & Tennis Courts ✩  Parcel Lockers ✩  Car Wash Station ✩  Grill Stations with Picnic Tables ✩  Fun Play Parks ✩  Online Rent Payments & Maintenance Requests ✩  Resident Referral Bonus ✩  Planned Community Events ✩  Active Duty Military & Federal Employee Discounts ✩  Professional Management & Maintenance Team ✩  Pool Pet Policy The Woods of Fairfax is a pet-friendly community - Fees and Restrictions apply - Call for details. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity RiV2X7Q5THTI",
