        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Pinebrook Apartments Rental Information Monthly Price: $1167 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 678 sq ft Lease Term: 12-Month Call our office at show contact info Apartment Amenities ✓ Cable Ready ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Disposal ✓ Eat-In Kitchen ✓ Gas Cooking Included ✓ Large Closets ✓ Refrigerator ✓ Separate Dining Area ✓ Wall-To-Wall Carpet ✓ Water & Sewer included Community Features ✓ 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance ✓ Assigned Parking ✓ Blocks to Landover Metro - Orange Line ✓ Close to Rt. 50 and Northwest Stadium ✓ Co-mingled Recycling Offered ✓ Near Metro bus Service ✓ On-site Laundry Room About Community Description: Pinebrook Apartments, where modern living meets unparalleled convenience. Nestled in a prime location near Rt. 50 and I-495, our community offers a gateway to seamless connectivity, ensuring you're just moments away from shopping, dining, and the vibrant energy of Washington, DC. Take a virtual tour through our photo gallery and envision a life of comfort and ease at Pinebrook Apartments. Your gateway to modern, convenient living awaits. Location: 2614 Pinebrook Ave. Landover, MD 20785 show contact info Office Hours: Monday - Friday, By Appointment Only Additional Information Call our office at show contact info Pet Policy: Pets - Max 2 allowed One time Fee $100.00, Rent $40.00, Cats - allowed Dogs - allowed Max weight 25 lb each, Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=pinebrook&rp=eRoTgc4gqBTV&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=pinebrook&rp=eRoTgc4gqBTV&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=pinebrook&rp=eRoTgc4gqBTV&t=trt All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY R7SH879MS6C7MRXE",
