        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post University Square 157 Westway Road, Greenbelt, MD, 20770 Call Now - show contact info x 133 OR Text 133 to show contact info to text our leasing team. Visit This Website to See More: https://lerner.aptsup.com/k5odeb Live better then ever at our beautifully wooded community in Greenbelt, Maryland. 1 bedroom | 1 bath | 892 square feet Features ✓  Pantry Cabinets ✓  Eat-In Kitchens in Most Apartments ✓  Renovated Apartment Homes ✓  Equipped Kitchens ✓  Walk-In Closets in All Apartments ✓  Modern Appliances ✓  Spacious Floor Plans ✓  In-Home Washers and Dryers ✓  Oversized, Private Balconies and Patios Community Features ✓  Convenient Location ✓  Pet-Friendly ✓  Resident-Exclusive Events ✓  Sparkling Swimming Pool ✓  Fitness Center ✓  Basketball Court ✓  Playground ✓  24/7 Maintenance ✓  Controlled Access Buildings ✓  Nearby Entertainment ✓  Plentiful, Free Parking Community Info Surrounded by acres of green space with mature landscaping and tall shade trees, Lerner University Square is a hidden gem in Greenbelt, Maryland. As a resident, you will have exclusive access to community amenities, such as a sparkling swimming pool, basketball court, and playground. Inside the apartments, you'll enjoy fully equipped kitchens, completely renovated with granite countertops and maple cabinets, and all apartments include a washer and dryer. With nearby access to the Greenbelt Metro/MARC and New Carrollton Metro/Amtrak Station and easy access to I-95 and the Capital Beltway, getting around town has never been so easy. If that weren't enough, we also have metro bus stops and a University of Maryland shuttle stop located within the community to take you to University of Maryland and other nearby shopping and dining destinations. Lerner University Square is the only community you should consider calling \"home\". Pet Policy Fee: $350 Rent: $50 Office Hours Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity izm8p7k