        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Description $1800/ month 1BR/1Bath/Balcony Location: Near Duke St and Van Dorn St, Alexandria, VA (5340 Holmes Run Pkwy) Easy access to I-395 for transit into DC, Arlington, or Springfield. Lots of windows and light - open floor plan. New kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances. Great balcony, 5th floor. Walk-in closet. Vinyl flooring. New HVAC system. Utilities (water & electric) included w/rent. Approx. 700 sq ft. • Pool • Gym • Laundry in the basement • 24 hour building security and front desk services. • 2 parking spots included • 1 Pet OK less than 20 pounds ($25 added / month for a pet). Close to shopping areas - Harris Teeter, Old Town Alexandria. Bus ride to metro. 1 month's rent security/damage deposit required (refundable). $1800 per month; pro-rate for partial month. $50 Application fee for background check. $350 move in fee ($100 refundable). Pets okay; $25/month added to rent for each pet. Building restricts to small pets only (cats, small dogs). 1+ year lease preferred Amenities Air Conditioning, Cable Ready, Heating, Smoke Free, Dishwasher, Disposal, Microwave, Kitchen, Granite Countertops, Refrigerator, Oven, Stainless Steel Appliances, Range, Freezer, Balcony, Views, Walk-In Closets, Vinyl Flooring If this ad is active, it is available now for showing and rent.",
