        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Foggy Bottom Spacious Studio w/Solarium Close to GWU, World Bank, IMF, GW Hospital 2141 I Street, NW #402, Washington, DC 20037 Introducing the Foggy Bottom Spacious Studio with Solarium (Perfect as a separate sleeping area) in the heart of Washington, DC, in Foggy Bottom. This charming studio boasts a prime location near GWU, the World Bank, and GW Hospital. The unit features a bright solarium, perfect for enjoying the city views. With parquet wood floors and large closets, this studio offers both style and functionality. Residents will also appreciate the convenience of the building's laundry facilities. Don't miss out on this opportunity to live in one of DC's most sought-after neighborhoods.435 sq ft. TAKE A YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR- youtu.be/9x_pnvk0zbQ 2141 I Street Northwest has a Walk Score of 98 out of 100. This location is a Walker’s Paradise so daily errands do not require a car. It is a three-minute walk from the Blue Metrorail Blue Line, the Orange Metrorail Orange Line, and the Silver Metrorail Silver Line at the FOGGY BOTTOM-GWU, BLUE/ORANGE/SILVER LINE CENTER PLATFORM stop. This location is in the Foggy Bottom - GWU - West End neighborhood in Washington, DC. Nearby parks include Alexander Pushkin Monument, Kogan Plaza, and George Washington University Plaza. Sorry, no pets. 12-month minimum lease. Unfurnished. Street Parking only. All adult applicants must apply and pass a credit check/background check as well as meet the income requirements. We accept and consider all sources of income towards qualification. The tenant is responsible for electricity as well as Internet/Cable. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. Co-signers are welcome; they apply just as you do. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. The first full month's rent, $200 non-refundable Move-In Fee, RBP Fee, and security deposit equal to one month's rent are due at lease signing. The unit is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. Luxury Foggy Bottom expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info no phone calls, please",
