        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Looking to rent out a couple of bedrooms to college students / folks looking for a place to stay. - This includes fully furnished bedrooms, kitchens, and bathrooms. - All utility is included (Verizon FIOS, Wifi Internet, Water, Gas, and Heat). - Verizon Fios & Internet (50MB/25MB) Commute Access: (Metro Bus Access to GMU & NOVA, & route to Pentagon & Vienna Metro Station) - Transportation access to the Metro Bus (Bus Route 29) is 1 minute in walking distance, which will take you to GMU Fairfax Campus / Vienna Metro Station or Pentagon Metro Station - 5 Minutes from NVCC (Annandale Campus) - 5 Minutes from GMU (Fairfax Campus) - 5 Minutes drive from the beltway Requirements: - Please pay one month up front (deposit) - Monthly rent depending on the term of the lease: Per Room Lease: -$1200 1 Year Lease (Large Room in the Basement) - $1000 1Year Lease (Large Room with Closet and Shared Bathroom) - $950 1 Year Lease (Mid Room with Closet and Shared Bathroom) - $850 1 Year Lease (Small Room downstairs with Shared Bathroom) *Note: For a month to month lease an additional $100 dollars will be added to the cost. Address: 3993 Champion Drive Annandale, VA 22003 Contact # show contact info",
