        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Langdon Park at Fort Washington 2428 Corning Ave Fort Washington, MD 20744 A wonderful home in Fort Washington is waiting for you! Call Today! show contact info We currently have a gorgeous 2 bedroom 1 bathroom with 960 sq ft. Monthly Price: $1688 - $1969 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Langdon Park at Fort Washington is a one-of-a-kind apartment living experience; a community and a home where those who walk through our doors find a comfortable and sustainable environment with meaningful opportunities. Led by a team of caring individuals who are committed to building a strong sense of community for their residents by offering unique resident enrichment activities and programs facilitated by certified teachers, healthcare workers, and local law enforcement professionals. Find the perfect place to call home with our pet-friendly spaces, available for rent in Fort Washington, Maryland. And with the best local hot spots - shopping, schools, dining, and entertainment - all within reach, you'll be proud to call Langdon Park at Fort Washington your new home! Contact us today and let the journey begin, on your way, to living life inspired. Community Highlights: ✓ Easy Freeway Access ✓ Fitness Center ✓ Pool ✓ Public Transportation ✓ Recycling ✓ *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ✓ Beautiful Landscaping ✓ Flexible Rent Payment Options with FLEX ✓ On-Site Maintenance ✓ On-Site Management Apartment Home Highlights: ✓ Central Heating and Air Conditioning ✓ Den/Study in Select Units ✓ Energy Efficient Lighting ✓ Health-Focused Air Filtration ✓ Washer/Dryer ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Patio/Balcony ✓ Programmable Thermostat ✓ Refrigerator ✓ Water Saving Fixtures Call Today! show contact info Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=langdon_park_at_fort_washington&rp=uBdU2daK4vCJ&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=langdon_park_at_fort_washington&rp=uBdU2daK4vCJ&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=langdon_park_at_fort_washington&rp=uBdU2daK4vCJ&t=trt Leasing Options: 12-Month Pet Policy: Max 2 allowed One-time Fee $250.00 Rent $35.00 Breed Restrictions Apply. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 97F4567DC9DC4F56",
