        "mainpic": "3ea9c8ab-2380-4f61-b262-ed9ad819b39d",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Brookland Ridge Apartments Visit our community today! 400 Taylor Street, NE Washington, DC 20017 Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Monthly Price: $2041 - $3956 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Type: 1-BR 1-BA Apartment Size: 772 sq ft Lease Terms: Call Pet Policy: Pets - Max 2 allowed, - One time Fee $400.00 - Rent $50.00 What you'll find in our community: ✓ Flexible Lease Terms ✓ Grill ✓ On-Site Parking ✓ On-site Recycling ✓ Picnic Area ✓ Playground ✓ Property Manager on Site ✓ Public Transportation ✓ Recycling ✓ Walk-Up ✓ 24- Hour Fitness Center with Free Weights ✓ Caring and Award Winning Staff ✓ Controlled-Access Buildings ✓ Convenient to Downtown, Capitol Hill, Catholic University, Children's Hospital, Washington Medical Center &amp Union Station ✓ Nearby Tennis Courts at Turkey Thicket Recreation ✓ Professional and Attentive Maintenance Staff ✓ Quiet Community in Wooded Setting ✓ Serene Picnic &amp Grilling Area For Entertaining ✓ Tranquil, Garden Style Living ✓ Within Blocks of Brookland-CUA Metro Description: One Month Free Rent! Nestled in a peaceful setting, Brookland Ridge Apartments invites you to enjoy comfort, convenience, and connection. These Brookland apartments in DC offer one and two-bedroom layouts with private balconies or terraces, full-size washer and dryer sets, and breakfast nooks in fully equipped kitchens. On-site perks like a 24-hour fitness center, picnic and grilling spaces, and a caring service team make every day feel smooth and simple. All of this just minutes from the Metro, local universities, and downtown. Contact us today and schedule a tour-we can't wait to welcome you to our community! This apartment comes with: ✓ Cable Ready ✓ Ceiling Fan ✓ Disposal ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Microwave ✓ Oven ✓ Range ✓ Smoke Free ✓ Tile Floors ✓ Window Coverings ✓ Ceramic Tile Floor ✓ Full Size Washer/Dryer in Every Apartment Home ✓ Fully Equipped Kitchens with Breakfast Nook ✓ Gas or Electric Range ✓ Generously Sized Floor Plans ✓ Plush Wall-To-Wall Carpeting ✓ Pre-wired for Cable and High-Speed Internet Access ✓ Private Balcony or Terrace ✓ Resident Controlled Heat and Air Conditioning ✓ Roommate Style Floorplans Available Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BrooklandRidgeApts Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=ppUcAp3QUSad&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=ppUcAp3QUSad&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=ppUcAp3QUSad&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY K64SHC0CRMXKD2X",
