luded. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Sat - Sun: - Newly reduce price of $1799.00 from $2074.00 Move-in by July 2nd, Independent Day special. Pet Policy: We are pet friendly. Pet Deposit $250 and Breed restrictions. Management Company: RES1 - Residential One Income Restrictions for Hancock Gardens # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $68,880       2 People   -   $78,720       3 People   -   $88,560       4 People   -   $98,340       5 People   -   $106,260 To qualify, annual income must not exceed amount noted in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the management office for more information. Affordable Housing - Income Restrictions Apply. Please contact office for more information. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY C9DD93A3666D41F",
