        "mainpic": "ec013a71-abf4-4fd6-81d1-18a3b9774111",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Surrey Square 6024 Surrey Square, Forestville, MD, 20747 Call Now - show contact info x 327 OR Text 327 to show contact info to chat! Need more information? Copy this link: https://lerner.aptsup.com/1q8y9m Apartment Living That Fits Your Life 3 bedroom | 2 bath | 1319 square feet Features ✓  Oversized, Private Balconies and Patios ✓  Eat-In Kitchens ✓  Renovated Kitchens* ✓  Granite Countertops* ✓  Wall-To-Wall Carpet ✓  Spacious Floor Plans ✓  Equipped Kitchens ✓  Furnished Apartments Available ✓  Abundant Closet Space ✓  Modern Appliances ✓  Oak Cabinets* Community Features ✓  Pet-Friendly ✓  Easy Access to Prince George's Community College and Forestville Military Academy ✓  Resident-Exclusive Events ✓  Near Reagan Washington National Airport and Andrews Air Force Base ✓  Minutes to Suitland Community Center ✓  BBQ and Picnic Area ✓  Close to the Suitland Metro with Metro Bus Stop at Community ✓  Great Location ✓  Easy Access to Washington, D.C.'s Greatest Landmarks and Nightlife ✓  Plentiful, Free Parking ✓  Olympic-Sized Swimming Pool ✓  Located on Pennsylvania Avenue Just Inside the Capital Beltway (I-495) ✓  Close to Shopping and Dining at Forest Village Park Mall ✓  Now Showing ✓  Two Playgrounds ✓  A Must See ✓  24/7 Maintenance ✓  Gated Community Community Info At Lerner Surrey Square, you will experience peaceful, garden-style living on Pennsylvania Avenue just minutes from Washington, D.C. If you're looking for recreational options, this lovely community includes a sparkling swimming pool, barbeque and picnic areas, two playgrounds, and it's adjacent to Park Berkshire. The spacious apartments include a private balcony or patio, wall-to-wall carpet, abundant closet space, fully equipped kitchens with modern appliances, and some were recently renovated with granite countertops and oak cabinets. You will appreciate the effortless access to the Capital Beltway, Route 4, and direct routing to the nearby Suitland Metro Station. Not only is Lerner Surrey Square situated near Samuel P. Massie, a top-rated elementary school, it is also in an ideal location for employees of Andrews Air Force Base, UPS, Verizon, Maryland Hospital Center, and the U.S. Census Bureau. Comfortable apartments, a great location, and unbeatable customer service are what will make you want to call Lerner Surrey Square home. Pet Policy Allowed | One time Fee $200 Rent $30 Restrictions: Lerner Surrey Square is a pet-friendly apartment community in Forestville, Maryland. A maximum of up to 2 pets per home are permitted and pet rent is applicable to each pet. The $200 pet fee per pet is non-refundable. Breed restrictions apply and no exotic pets. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity 84Ucr0Kb",
