        "mainpic": "299836a3-6869-4f4f-9f33-37d86e293441",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Quebec Arms Apartments 1400 Merrimac Dr Hyattsville, MD 20783 Monthly Price: $1575 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 683 sq ft Call Today! show contact info One Month Free Features in this apartment home: ➢ Beautiful hardwood floors, some carpeted apartment homes ➢ Garbage Disposal ➢ Generous room sizes ➢ High Speed Internet Access ➢ Individually controlled heating and air conditioning ➢ Mini blinds in all windows ➢ One, two, and three bedroom apartment homes ➢ Spacious Closets About the community: When it comes to selecting the perfect home, one size doesn't fit all. If you're looking for an affordable apartment home that meets all your needs, look no further. We believe apartment living should offer value, comfort and convenience. Choose from a selection of one, two and three bedroom floor plans. Once you find the match that fits your needs, you'll quickly discover that each of our floor plans were crafted to guarantee you get the most value per square foot. Our homes offer all the little things that make life easier. From large living spaces to the ample closet space, our apartments are sure to impress! Experience the perfect balance of space and accessibility in this oversized one-bedroom apartment at Quebec Arms. Unlike the cramped new builds in the area, our floor plans are designed with real living in mind, featuring a sprawling living room that easily fits a full furniture set and a dedicated dining area for home-cooked meals. You will love the massive walk-in closets that provide all the storage you have been looking for and the large windows that flood the space with natural light. Our location is a commuter's dream, situated just a short trip from the West Hyattsville Metro station and the vibrant Arts District. Whether you are heading to UMD or downtown DC, getting around is effortless with easy access to major transit and the Northwest Branch Trail. Hablamos Espanol. Our professional on-site management team is dedicated to providing excellent service, and we are proud to offer full bilingual support as we speak Spanish. Come tour your new home today and see why Quebec Arms is the hidden gem of Hyattsville. Income guidelines apply. Qualification is based on household size and verified income. Please contact the leasing office for details Amenities at our property: ➢ 1 block to Metro ➢ Controlled Access ➢ On-site management ➢ Playground ➢ Some Paid Utilities ➢ Central laundry facility ➢ Close to Downtown Silver Spring and DC ➢ On-site Maintenance ➢ Shuttlebus service to University of MD ➢ Walking distance to shopping center Additional information: Call Today! show contact info Terms: 12-Month Pets: No pets allowed; Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=qrbsPvkCuizo&t=wb 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=qrbsPvkCuizo&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=qrbsPvkCuizo&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 81BF749197D248D",
