        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1541 - $1671 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Potomac Woods Senior Living: 2001 Southhampton St Woodbridge, VA 22191 Apartment for Rent: 2-BR 2-BA | Square Feet: 754 - 954 sq ft | Lease Length: 12-Month Call us at show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES − Affordable Housing − Disability Access − Fitness Center − Guest Parking − Lounge − Onsite Management − Senior Housing − Shopping Nearby − Smoke-Free − Verizon FiOS − 24-hour Emergency Maintenance − Community Room with Kitchen − Community/Onsite Parking − Emergency Maintenance − Game Room with Billiards Table − On-site Beauty Salon − Planned Community Activities − Public Transportation − Recycling Available − Section 8 Vouchers Accepted APARTMENT AMENITIES − Air Conditioning − Carpet − Central Heat and Air − Dishwasher − Elevator(s) − Mini Blinds − View − Walk In Closet(s) − Washer & Dryer Connections − Washer Dryer Hookup − Contemporary finishes − Emergency pull cords, sprinklers, smoke detectors − Fully-equipped all elecric kitchens ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Senior living with respect! Sited on four beautifully wooded acres in Woodbridge, VA, Potomac Woods Senior Living Community offers convenience, comfort, and community for independent seniors. Designed for affordable, independent senior living, this three-story, controlled access elevator building features one and two-bedroom pet-friendly apartment living. Each apartment home is fully equipped with wall-to-wall carpeting, all electric kitchens with dishwashers, individually controlled heating and air conditioning, washer and dryer hookups, and available balconies. A large Resident Lounge on the lobby level has a kitchen for resident functions or large group entertaining. Residents also have complimentary access to a craft and game room, library, and exercise facility. The beautifully landscaped outdoor spaces, patio and resident gardens are ideal for enjoying nature. Age & Income restrictions apply. Pet Policy: Allowed: Small pets (under 25 lbs). Deposit: $200. Monthly Pet Rent: $25. Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=potomac_woods_senior_living&rp=ud32iTrLHKL4&t=wb Call us at show contact info All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY ED168407A53E4E",
