        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Fabulous 2-bed 2-bath apartment in Adams Morgan Welcome to the fabulous 2-bed 2-bath apartment in Adams Morgan, a gem nestled in the heart of Washington, DC. This apartment boasts two spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms, offering ample space for your comfort and convenience. The interior is beautifully designed with hardwood floors that add a touch of elegance and warmth to the space. The living area is filled with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere that you'll love coming home to. The apartment also features an in-unit washer and dryer, making laundry day a breeze. One of the standout features of this apartment is the exposed brick walls, adding a unique, rustic charm to the space. This apartment is not just a place to live, but a lifestyle. Experience the best of Washington, DC, living in the fabulous 2-bed 2-bath apartment in Adams Morgan. 676 sq ft. TAKE A YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR - https://youtu.be/8NFj6hbZFLk 1951 Biltmore Street Northwest has a Walk Score of 87 out of 100. This location is Very Walkable, so most errands can be accomplished on foot. It is an eight-minute walk from the RD Red at the WOODLEY PARK-ZOO/ADAMS MORGAN, RED LINE CENTER PLATFORM stop. This location is in the Adams Morgan neighborhood in Washington, DC. Nearby parks include Walter Pierce Park, Kalorama, and Kalorama Park. Close to Safeway and Harris Teeter Supermarkets, SVS, and a few blocks away is all the nightlife with Bars and Resturants. 12-month minimum lease. Cats are warmly welcomed with a one-time pet fee of $250 per cat. Sorry, dogs. Unfurnished. Tentas pays electric and 25% of the building's water. All adult applicants must apply and pass a credit check/background check, as well as meet the income requirements. We accept and consider all sources of income towards qualification. Co-Signers are welcome. Street Parking only. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. Co-signers are welcome. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. NO MOVE-IN FEES! The first full month's rent, RBP Fee, and security deposit equal to one month's rent are due at lease signing. Luxury Adams Morgan expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact us for requests for showings by emailing me. THIS IS A PRIVATE LISTING",
