        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Centrally Located Dupont Circle at the Imperial House 1 Bedroom in the heart of it all! 1601 18th Street, NW #406, Washington, DC 20009 FOR SALE OR RENT. In the heart of Dupont, only a block away from the Circle. Make the Imperial House your new home. This one-bedroom, one-bath apartment is available at the Imperial House Condominiums. Beautiful floors and Great Natural Light streaming in. Upscale shutters on the sliding living room doors. Spacious living area. The unit has a walk-in closet for great storage or use as a \"Zoom Room\" Home Office space. The kitchen has great counter space with a dishwasher. The bedroom will fit a queen-size bed nicely. Washer & Dryer in the Building, Utilities included.. 651 sq ft Street Parking only Amenities at Imperial House include a 24-hour front desk, a rooftop deck with sweeping views of the city, a gym/yoga/meditation room, and common laundry & bike storage. YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR- youtu.be/7E5jTVZRbgc Walk to Dupont Circle Metro (Red Line), Safeway, Starbucks, Krispy Kreme Donuts, Whole Foods, Trader Joe's, and many more shops and restaurants just a short walk. All utilities included (except, cable, internet. Unit Professionally Managed by Chatel Real Estate, Inc. ChatelRealEstate.com THIS UNIT IS FOR SALE 369K OR RENT. Contact the agent for details. 12-month+ minimum lease. Unfurnished. Sorry, no pets. Co-signers are welcome; they apply just as you do. All adult applicants must apply and pass a credit check/background check, as well as meet the income requirements. We accept and consider all sources of income towards qualification. Tenant pays cable/Internet. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. We accept and consider all sources of income. The first full month's rent, RBP Fee, security deposit equal to one month's rent, and building move-in fees $350/$250 deposit are due at lease signing. The unit is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. Luxury Dupont expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info , no phone calls please.",
