nant pays 33.33% of the building's water, 100% of unit gas and electricity, plus cable/Internet. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. Co-signers are welcome; they apply just as you do if you have one. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. We accept and consider all sources of income. The first full month's rent, RBP Fee, and security deposit equal to one month's rent, are due at lease signing. The building is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. Luxury Dupont-Logan expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info , no phone calls please.",
