        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 1510 Q St NW, # 1, Washington, DC 20009 Discover this delightful lower-level 1 Bedroom Gem in the heart of Dupont/Logan Circles-FURNISHED OPTION This unit comes furnished or unfurnished. You chose! Discover this delightful lower-level 1-bedroom, 1-bath apartment in the Dupont/Logan Circle neighborhoods. Upon the front entry, you will note the hardwood floors throughout the unit. The apartment has light gleaming in the south-facing living room. The living room features a decorative fireplace that opens to the galley kitchen. A gas range is perfect for the chef-inspired meals for you, and a dishwasher for clean up. Plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen. Off the kitchen is the rear entry to your unit. On the north side of the apartment, you will find the Bedroom that will fit a queen bed nicely. The bathroom has a beautiful marble-tiled, large shower. The unit has a free washer and dryer just outside your door, including a fridge for community use. Sq footage is 650. Street parking only. TAKE A YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR- youtu.be/GYJ_oDZbumo 1510 Q Street Northwest has a Walk Score of 98 out of 100. This location is a Walker’s Paradise, so daily errands do not require a car. It is a nine-minute walk from the Red Metrorail Red Line at the DUPONT CIRCLE, RED LINE TRACK 2 PLATFORM stop. This location is in the Dupont Circle neighborhood near Logan Circle in Washington, DC. Nearby parks include Stead Playground, Stead, and Hahnemann Memorial. Whole Foods Grocery is just a few blocks away, as well as all the restaurants on 14th and 17th Streets. FURNISHED OPTION- Same rate, Unit comes with sofa, dining table & chairs, bookcase, queen bed & mattress, dresser and a recliner chair. NO MOVE IN FEES! 12-month minimum lease. No short-term leases. Sorry, no pets. All adult applicants must apply and pass a credit check/background check, as well as meet the income requirements. We accept and consider all sources of income towards qualification. Tenant pays 33.33% of the building's water, 100% of unit gas and electricity, plus cable/Internet. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. Co-signers are welcome; they apply just as you do if you have one. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. We accept and consider all sources of income. The first full month's rent, RBP Fee, and security deposit equal to one month's rent, are due at lease signing. The building is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. Luxury Dupont-Logan expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info , no phone calls please.",
