        "geocode_query": "4422 Greenwich Parkway NW, Washington",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Spacious Elegant 6 Br/3 1/2 bath Tudor Townhouse w/Deck close to Georgetown University & Hospital 4422 Greenwich Parkway NW, Washington, DC 20007 Welcome to this spacious 6-bedroom, 3.5 bathroom Tudor townhouse located in the Georgetown area in Foxhall Village. This large, charming home features hardwood floors throughout, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere. Light filled Living and Dining rooms. The kitchen features a gas range perfect for those gourmet meals and a dishwasher for clean up. Your bedroom quarters are on the upper levels. 3 bedrooms on the second level with a renovated bathroom. The primary bedroom has 3 closets plus a window bench seat perfect for curling up with a good book. The top floor, with its sloped roof line, has two more bedrooms with a full bathroom. The basement has your 6th bedroom with a full bath, as well as laundry and storage. With 4 tandem parking spaces included, you'll never have to worry about finding a spot after a long day. Step outside onto the deck and take in the fresh air or relax in the private yard. Located close to Georgetown University/Hospital and the French/German Embassies, this townhouse offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Radiator heat and window A/C. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this beautiful house your new home. 2,252 Total square feet. TAKE A YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR - https://youtu.be/ale7fFsSIok First Level: Entry, Living Room (15' 3\" x 13' 8\"), Dining Room (12' 3\" x 18'), Kitchen, Powder 1/2 bath Room, and access to Deck/Backyard/Parking. Second Level: Three Bedrooms (Primary-17' x 12', #2- 11' x 10' 7\" also #3- 7'3\" x 12' 6\") and Hall Bathroom. Third Level: Two Bedrooms ( 13' x 12' 6\" & 18' x 12' 7\") and Hall Bathroom Lower Level: One Bedroom (9'x18\") with full Bath plus Storage Area and Laundry. 4422 Greenwich Parkway Northwest has a Walk Score of 54 out of 100. This location is Somewhat Walkable so some errands can be accomplished on foot. It is in the Foxhall-Palisades neighborhood in Washington, DC. Nearby parks include Hardy Playground, Hardy, and Archbold Parkway. 12-month+ minimum lease. Unfurnished. Sorry, no pets. Co-signers are welcome; they apply just as you do. All adult applicants must apply and pass a credit check/background check, as well as meet the income requirements. We accept and consider all sources of income towards qualification. Tenant pays electric, gas, water, and lawn maintenance. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. We accept and consider all sources of income. The first full month's rent, RBP Fee, security deposit equal to one month's rent, and cable/internet are due at lease signing. The unit is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. ChatelRealEstate.com Luxury Georgetown expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info , no phone calls please.",
