        "geocode_query": "",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Great Studio in Glover Park/North Georgetown w/Murphy Bed, Walk-In Closet, Eat in Kitchen! 3925 Davis Place, NW #B6, Washington, DC 20007 Welcome to this charming, large studio condo located in the heart of Glover Park and North Georgetown. This unit features parquet wood floors, a convenient Murphy bed, a coat closet, and a spacious walk-in closet with built-ins. It has a separate eat-in kitchen with a gas range, dishwasher, and granite countertops. With a washer and dryer located in the building, laundry day will be a breeze. Window A/C and radiator heat. 460 Sq. Ft. This unit is perfect for those seeking a convenient and affordable living space in a desirable, quiet neighborhood. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this Glover Park gem your new home. Contact Craig today to schedule a tour! TAKE A YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR - youtu.be/Nho9HH7DWHM 3925 Davis Place Northwest is in the Glover Park neighborhood. Glover Park is the 22nd most walkable neighborhood in Washington, DC with a neighborhood Walk Score of 79. Close to Bus lines to Georgetown University and American University. Nearby parks include Stoddert Recreation Center and ballpark. Close to Safeway, Trader Joe's, Whole Food Supermarkets, Stoddert Recreation Center/Ballpark. and many restaurants. Cats are warmly welcome with a one-time pet fee of $250.00. Dogs are warmly welcome with a one-time pet fee of $450.00 on a case-by-case basis. Size (less than 50 pounds) and breed restrictions. Unfurnished but comes with a built-in Murphy Bed. 12-Month Minimum lease. Street parking only. The tenant is responsible for electric and cable/Internet. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. Co-signers are welcome. The application fee/credit check is $53 per person and the application may be completed on our website. We accept and consider all sources of income. The first full month's rent, Building Move-in/out Fee $300 non-refundable, Pet Fees, RBP Fee, and a security deposit equal to one month's rent are due at lease signing. The unit is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. Luxury expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info",
