        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Arlington Gazebo Love, One Bedroom Close to Everything near Ballston 4635 20th Road, North #5, Arlington, VA 22207 Discover Arlington Gazebo Love at The Dominion Terrace Condominiums, a well-appointed one-bedroom, one-bath condo conveniently located near Ballston. Spacious living and dining room. Updated flooring throughout the unit and new paint. This unit features a stainless steel fridge and a dishwasher in the galley kitchen for easy meal prep and cleanup. The bedroom will fit a king-size bed with a mirrored double closet. Building amenities include on-site washer/dryer facilities in the complex, bike storage, extra storage, and off-street parking for added convenience. Situated close to shops, dining, and transit options, this condo offers a practical, comfortable base for everyday living in Arlington. 588 sq. ft. TAKE A YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR- https://youtu.be/7P9Nu-zcSxE 4635 20th Road North has a Walk Score of 82 out of 100. This location is Very Walkable, so most errands can be accomplished on foot. This location is in the Waverly Hills neighborhood in Arlington. Nearby parks include Woodstock Park, Clarenford Station Park, and Cherry Valley Park, Arlington, VA. Ballston Metro is only 1.5 miles away. PETS- requires the Condo Board of Directors' approval. If approved, small dogs are warmly welcome with a one-time pet fee of $450.00, and cats $250 on a case-by-case basis. Unfurnished 12-Month Minimum lease. One (1) Off-street parking space included. The tenant is responsible for electric and cable/Internet. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. Co-signers are welcome; they apply just as you do. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. We accept and consider all sources of income. The first full month's rent, Pet Fees, RBP Fee, and a security deposit equal to one month's rent are due at lease signing. The unit is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. Luxury expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman and Lou Costanza, with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info -office. No phone calls please.",
