        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 740 Quebec Place, NW #1, Main Floor, Washington, DC 20010 Precious Petworth 1 Bedroom Apartment with Patio and yard; Decorative Fireplace Welcome to your new Petworth home in the heart of Washington, DC! This 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom main floor apartment, offers a blend of comfort and style. The apartment is designed with a light-filled living area that creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The decorative fireplace adds a touch of elegance and coziness to the living area, and the unit has brand-new carpet. The large kitchen has a huge kitchen island, perfect for the chef in you! The light-filled bedroom will fit a queen-size bed. The apartment also features an in-unit portable washer and dryer, adding convenience to your daily routine. The back patio is a perfect spot for relaxation, offering an outdoor space to enjoy the city's beautiful weather and plant some herbs. Being close to the Metro, this apartment is not just a place to live, but a place to love. Experience the best of city living in this charming apartment in Petworth. Approx. 492 Sq Ft. NEW! TAKE A YOUTUBE VIDEO TOUR- https://youtu.be/n-41hDHioUs 740 Quebec Place Northwest has a Walk Score of 88 out of 100. This location is Very Walkable, so most errands can be accomplished on foot. It is a two-minute walk from the GR Green at the GEORGIA AVE-PETWORTH, GREEN/YELLOW LINE CENTER PLATFORM stop. Nearby parks include Parkview, Parkview Playground, and Parkview Recreation Center. Sorry, no pets. 12-month minimum lease. Unfurnished. Street Parking only. All adult applicants must apply and pass a credit check/background check as well as meet the income requirements. We accept and consider all sources of income towards qualification. The tenant is responsible for 100% electricity, 33% of building gas and water as well as 100% of Internet/Cable. Additional Resident Benefits Package (RBP) $30 per month. Co-signers are welcome. The application fee/credit check is $54 per person, and the application may be completed on our website. The first full month's rent, RBP Fee, and security deposit equal to one month's rent, are due at lease signing. The unit is professionally managed by Chatel Real Estate. Luxury expertise brought to you by Craig Shireman, “Craig the Châtel Château Specialist” with Chatel Real Estate, Inc. Please contact for requests for showings by emailing show contact info , no phone calls, please",
