        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Amherst Square 2315 Blueridge Ave #14 Wheaton, MD 20902 Phone: show contact info Apartment Information: 1 - 4 Bedroom | 1 - 1.5 Bath Apartment Size: 820 - 1300 sq ft Monthly Price: $1591 - $2500 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Includes: ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Central Air Conditioning ◾ Classic Refinished Wood Flooring ◾ Formal Dining Room ◾ Full Kitchen with Window ◾ Garbage Disposal ◾ High Speed Internet Available ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Storage and Closet Space Property Description: \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" Amherst Square is a community that has a prime location boasting many conveniences and amenities! Within steps to the metro, shopping and minutes to DC, Amherst Square combines value and convenience together for easy living! Property Amenities: ◾ Community Center ◾ Easy access to I-495,I-270,I-95 ◾ Easy Access to Major Roadways ◾ Laundry Facility ◾ Playground ◾ Convenient to MARC commuter train ◾ Convenient to nearby Silver Spring, Takoma Park, and Washington D.C. ◾ Near Retail, Restaurants and Entertainment ◾ Walk to Wheaton Metro (Red Line) Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=amherst_square&rp=mto5YsTfvDiu&t=wb Phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: $25 monthly pet rent. $350 deposit per pet nonrefundable. Income Restrictions for Amherst Square # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $49,260       2 People   -   $56,280       3 People   -   $63,300       4 People   -   $70,320       5 People   -   $75,960       6 People   -   $81,600 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. Income Limits Apply - Please ask a Leasing Consultant for details. Minimum Income Requirements: 1 Bedroom - $37,740 2 Bedroom - $44,460 3 B