        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Lex at Waterfront Station 1151 4th Street SW Washington, DC 20024 Office Phone: show contact info . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: Efficiency BR - 1 BA - 300 - 400 sq ft Monthly Price: $3146 - $4122 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: Variable . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Welcome to Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station apartments in the heart of Southwest Waterfront! As part of Bernstein Management Corporation, you can count on a few things - an enjoyable D.C. neighborhood, great apartments and a friendly, helpful team focused on making your life easier. We want to ensure your experience at Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station is hassle-free, so all you have to worry about is where to put your couch. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: ✓ 24/7 concierge ✓ 24/7 emergency maintenance ✓ 24/7 fitness center with studio ✓ Controlled access ✓ Courtyard with grills ✓ Garage parking ✓ On-site management ✓ Package acceptance ✓ Resident lounge and game room ✓ Rooftop deck with pool and grills ✓ Shared workspace with printing ✓ Nearby Capital Bikeshare and Zipcar ✓ Next to the Waterfront Metro station . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment Home Comes With: ✓ Air Conditioning ✓ Hardwood Floor ✓ High Ceilings in select units ✓ Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ Walk In Closet(s) ✓ Floor-to-ceiling windows ✓ Frameless glass-enclosed showers ✓ Full-size energy efficient washer & dryer ✓ Granite countertops with subway tile backsplash ✓ Moveable kitchen island with extra cabinets ✓ Open pocket doors ✓ Remote operated bedroom ceiling fans . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Office Phone: -- show contact info -- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LexandLeoApartments Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=87FaCVZkBX9T&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=87FaCVZkBX9T&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=87FaCVZkBX9T&t=sch Pets: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. We also have a dog park and pet spa so your furry friends can live the good life too. Pet Move-in Fee - $500. $55 Monthly Fee Per Pet Maximum of two pets per apartment. Breed restrictions may apply. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Bernstein Management Corporation will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person if the rental payment, whole or part, will be provided through a voucher for rent housing assistance from the District, state or federal government. Rental rates and availability are subject to change. Equal Housing Opportunity. Specials and availability are subject to change without notice. Restrictions apply. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY B9GKKKEVT00NHL4",
