gy efficient washer & dryer ✓ Granite countertops with subway tile backsplash ✓ Moveable kitchen island with extra cabinets ✓ Open pocket doors ✓ Remote operated bedroom ceiling fans . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Office Phone: -- show contact info -- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LexandLeoApartments Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=87FaCVZkBX9T&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=87FaCVZkBX9T&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=87FaCVZkBX9T&t=sch Pets: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. We also have a dog park and pet spa so your furry friends can live the good life too. Pet Move-in Fee - $500. $55 Monthly Fee Per Pet Maximum of two pets per apartment. Breed restrictions may apply. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Bernstein Management Corporation will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person if the rental payment, whole or part, will be provided through a voucher for rent housing assistance from the District, state or federal government. Rental rates and availability are subject to change. Equal Housing Opportunity. Specials and availability are subject to change without notice. Restrictions apply. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY B9GKKKEVT00NHL4",
