        "mainpic": "b7814536-2133-4af7-8362-098f82e0222c",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Lex at Waterfront Station Located at: 1151 4th Street SW Washington, DC 20024 Featured apartment home: Efficiency bed | 1 bath | 395 sq ft Base monthly rent: $1397 Total Monthly Price: $1397 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Call Today! show contact info Welcome to Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station apartments in the heart of Southwest Waterfront! As part of Bernstein Management Corporation, you can count on a few things - an enjoyable D.C. neighborhood, great apartments and a friendly, helpful team focused on making your life easier. We want to ensure your experience at Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station is hassle-free, so all you have to worry about is where to put your couch. Household income must be verified to match property income restrictions. Two most recent tax returns, six most recent bank statements for all accessible bank accounts and proof of all additional income is required (i.e. self-employment, recurring gifts, social security). If needed, other documentation may be requested. Wonderful Amenities! ● 24/7 concierge ● 24/7 emergency maintenance ● 24/7 fitness center with studio ● Controlled access ● Courtyard with grills ● Garage parking ● On-site management ● Package acceptance ● Resident lounge and game room ● Rooftop deck with pool and grills ● Shared workspace with printing ● Nearby Capital Bikeshare and Zipcar ● Next to the Waterfront Metro station Apartment Features! ● 24/7 concierge ● 24/7 fitness center with studio ● Attached garage parking ● Bike storage with repair station ● Courtyard with grills ● Dog park and spa ● Dry cleaning lockers ● Next to the Waterfront Metro station ● Package acceptance ● Resident lounge ● Rooftop deck with grills and pool ● Shared workspace with printing ● Air conditioning ● Appliances Included ● Open-concept layout ● Tile backsplash ● Washer and dryer in-home Hours: Tue - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 2:00 PM Call Today! show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LexandLeoApartments Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=bb4qb39JENgP&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=bb4qb39JENgP&t=sch Terms: Variable Pet Policy: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. We also have a dog park and pet spa so your furry friends can live the good life too. Pet Move-in Fee - $500. $55 Monthly Fee Per Pet Maximum of two pets per apartment. Breed restrictions may apply. Bernstein Management Corporation will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person if the rental payment, whole or part, will be provided through a voucher for rent housing assistance from the District, state or federal government. Rental rates and availability are subject to change. Equal Housing Opportunity. Specials and availability are subject to change without notice. Restrictions apply. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 89F7BCFD97ED442",
