        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to The Villas at Langley! Located at: 8100 15th Ave Hyattsville, MD 20783 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 1 # of Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 787 sq ft Monthly Price: $1315 - $1428 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call for details: show contact info What makes a place feel like home? It's all the special little things in the home, community, and neighborhood. Those features and conveniences that fit your lifestyle and how you want to live. The best of life is yours at Haven Largo-appealing amenities, ample entertaining areas, private outdoor spaces, and attentive maintenance and management at the ready. Explore the details that define the Haven Largo experience. Special-Especial Move in by 7/7/26 & receive 1 month free + waived prorated rent on select homes. Exclusions may apply. Contact the leasing office for details. Mundate antes del 7/7/26 y recibe hasta 1 mes gratuito en viviendas seleccionadas. Pueden aplicarse exclusiones. Ponte en contacto con la oficina de arrendamiento para obtener mas detalles. Community Features: ◾ 24 Hour Access ◾ 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance ◾ Basketball Court ◾ Enclosed Soccer Field ◾ Large Swimming Pool ◾ Laundry Centers in Each Building ◾ Online Services ◾ Outdoor BBQ Grills ◾ Playground ◾ Property Manager on Site ◾ 1 Mile from the Adelphi Recreation Center ◾ CASA de Maryland On-Site ◾ Close to Langley Park - McCormick Elementary School ◾ Easy Access to MD Rt 2, MD 313 and MD 235 ◾ Easy Access to Public Transportation ◾ Hospitals Nearby: Washington Adventist Hospital and Holy Cross Hospital ◾ Park-Like Community with Outdoor Seating ◾ Shopping Nearby: Langely Park Plaza, Prince George's Plaza and K-Mart Apartment Home Features: ◾ Central Air Conditioning ◾ Dens Available ◾ Garbage Disposal ◾ Gas Cooking ◾ Gas Heat ◾ Large, Eat-In Kitchen in select units ◾ Patio or Balcony Available ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Separate Dining Room ◾ Tub/Shower Office Hours: Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Wed: 11:00 AM - 5:30 PM Thu - Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Call for details: show contact info Pet Policy: Max 2 Allowed | One time Fee $250 | Rent $25 Restrictions: Breed Restrictions Apply Leasing Options: 12-Month Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=oR3iQVKqKaMs&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=oR3iQVKqKaMs&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 7258DAEC7B6740C",
