        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Haven Reston 11012 Becontree Lake Dr Reston, VA 20190 Monthly Price: $1891 - $1951 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 816 sq ft Call Today! show contact info Features in this apartment home: ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Carpet ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Disposal ➢ Hardwood Flooring ➢ Oven/Range ➢ Tub/Shower ➢ Air Conditioning ➢ Large windows offering ample natural light ➢ Plush carpeting ➢ Private balconies and patios ➢ Refrigerator/Freezer ➢ Select newly renovated apartments with goose-neck faucets, tile backsplashes, quartz countertops, vinyl hardwood plank flooring, and in-home washers and dryers ➢ Variety of apartment styles with black, white, and limited stainless steel finishes ➢ Versatile one- and two-bedroom floor plans with one-bedroom-den options ➢ White and oak cabinetry options About the community: Join a welcoming, garden-style community with a wide selection of affordable floor plans and an array of bright recreation spaces that let you live life to the fullest. Our proactive management and maintenance teams are committed to ensuring your experience is as carefree and enjoyable as possible. Amenities at our property: ➢ 24-hour maintenance ➢ Central laundry ➢ Children's playground ➢ Dedicated on-site management team ➢ Fenced bark park ➢ On-site storage units ➢ Outdoor sport court ➢ Package Receiving ➢ Surface parking ➢ Tennis Court ➢ *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ➢ 24-hour fitness center with cardio equipment ➢ Convenient clubhouse and resident lounge ➢ Lush setting on 48 acres of pristine woodlands ➢ Minutes from Dulles Toll Road, Fairfax County Parkway, and Dulles International Airport ➢ Serene swimming pool with lounge seating, patio tables, and umbrellas ➢ Sun-drenched courtyard and grilling patio with social seating ➢ Within two miles of Wiehle-Reston East Metro on the Silver Line Additional information: Call Today! show contact info Terms: 12-Month Pets: Haven Reston is a paw-friendly community. Cats and dogs are permitted with the payment of an additional $50 per month in rent. Two pets are allowed per residence, and breed restrictions apply. Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=haven_reston&rp=wYSjj2shrhPK&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=haven_reston&rp=wYSjj2shrhPK&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=haven_reston&rp=wYSjj2shrhPK&t=trt If you are interested in applying for one of our apartment homes, we require the following documents at the time of application. Each household differs and may require further documents than what is listed below. Our team will contact you after application submission if further documentation or clarification is needed. Your timely response to documentation requests will prevent any lengthy delays in the processing of your application. Proof of Income: 4 Most Recent Consecutive Paystubs Tax return for the last two years 1099 Form Benefit letter social security administration. (Retired, Disability) 401K Most Current Bank Statement. Proof of Child Support: Child Support Statement or Court Order of Child Support All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 48C4435D836147",
