        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 1815 17th St NW, Washington, DC 20009 Immerse yourself in the heart of Washington, DC. Located on the 17th Street Corridor near Logan and 14th in the coveted Dupont Circle neighborhood, The Croydon is a classic Art Deco high-rise that offers access to many of DC’s best restaurants, shopping, and entertainment destinations – all just steps from your front door. Choose from a number of open studio floor plans, complete with beautiful parquet floors, spacious closets, and individually controlled heating and air conditioning. Fantastic for on-the-go lifestyles, you can combine the best of adventure and the comforts of home at The Croydon. Apartment Features: White Quartz Stone Countertops Walk-Through Closets with Solid Wood Shelving Contemporary Hardware & Fixtures with Satin Finish Simulated Wood LVP Flooring Original Oak Parquet Flooring Walk-Through Closets with Customizable Track Shelving Gas Cooking GE Appliances including Gas Stove and Microwave White Shaker Cabinets Oversized Double-Paned Windows Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithborger.com/e2xqp5dc/croydon We will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person because the person will provide the rental payment, in whole or in part, through a voucher for rental housing assistance provided by the District or federal government. Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
