        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Available July 10th, 2026 for a responsible working adult. This is a quiet, peaceful rooming house atmosphere near Briley Pkwy & Clarksville Pike, less than a mile off Briley Pkwy in N.W. Albany. Quiet safe area with a furnished room, off-street parking for one operational vehicle per tenant. Common areas include a living room with a 54\" TV and Roku, dining room, kitchen with cookware, plates, cups, glasses, and cutlery. Washer and dryer, WiFi, basketball half court, BBQ, and fire pit. You must be employed, have a driver's license and a vehicle. Week runs Sunday through Saturday. Rent is $1,200 per week, with a $250 nonrefundable deposit plus first week due at move-in. Tenants are responsible for gas and electric; owner covers water and trash. If interested, reply with your name and best way to reach you.",
