        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Surrey Square 6024 Surrey Square, Forestville, MD, 20747 Use this link for more info: https://lerner.aptsup.com/1y0kwd Call Now - show contact info x 326 OR Text 326 to show contact info to text us. Apartment Living That Fits Your Life 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath | Approximately 950 Sq. Ft. Community Info: At Lerner Surrey Square, you will experience peaceful, garden-style living on Pennsylvania Avenue just minutes from Washington, D.C. If you're looking for recreational options, this lovely community includes a sparkling swimming pool, barbeque and picnic areas, two playgrounds, and it's adjacent to Park Berkshire. The spacious apartments include a private balcony or patio, wall-to-wall carpet, abundant closet space, fully equipped kitchens with modern appliances, and some were recently renovated with granite countertops and oak cabinets. You will appreciate the effortless access to the Capital Beltway, Route 4, and direct routing to the nearby Suitland Metro Station. Not only is Lerner Surrey Square situated near Samuel P. Massie, a top-rated elementary school, it is also in an ideal location for employees of Andrews Air Force Base, UPS, Verizon, Maryland Hospital Center, and the U.S. Census Bureau. Comfortable apartments, a great location, and unbeatable customer service are what will make you want to call Lerner Surrey Square home.   Unit Highlights ✧  Oak Cabinets* ✧  Equipped Kitchens ✧  Furnished Apartments Available ✧  Granite Countertops* ✧  Abundant Closet Space ✧  Modern Appliances ✧  Spacious Floor Plans ✧  Renovated Kitchens* ✧  Wall-To-Wall Carpet ✧  Eat-In Kitchens ✧  Oversized, Private Balconies and Patios Community Highlights ✧  A Must See ✧  Close to Shopping and Dining at Forest Village Park Mall ✧  Plentiful, Free Parking ✧  Minutes to Suitland Community Center ✧  Easy Access to Prince George's Community College and Forestville Military Academy ✧  Gated Community ✧  Pet-Friendly ✧  BBQ and Picnic Area ✧  Easy Access to Washington, D.C.'s Greatest Landmarks and Nightlife ✧  24/7 Maintenance ✧  Near Reagan Washington National Airport and Andrews Air Force Base ✧  Great Location ✧  Olympic-Sized Swimming Pool ✧  Located on Pennsylvania Avenue Just Inside the Capital Beltway (I-495) ✧  Now Showing ✧  Resident-Exclusive Events ✧  Two Playgrounds ✧  Close to the Suitland Metro with Metro Bus Stop at Community Office Hours Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Pet Policy Allowed | One time Fee $200 Rent $30 Restrictions: Lerner Surrey Square is a pet-friendly apartment community in Forestville, Maryland. A maximum of up to 2 pets per home are permitted and pet rent is applicable to each pet. The $200 pet fee per pet is non-refundable. Breed restrictions apply and no exotic pets. Equal Housing Opportunity EupVlW3edI6t",
