        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Pinebrook Apartments Call our office at show contact info Apartment Details: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Footage: 678 sq ft Monthly Price: $1167 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 12-Month Apartment Features: ◾ Air Conditioning ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Disposal ◾ Gas Cooking Included ◾ Hardwood Floors ◾ Large Closets ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Wall-To-Wall Carpet ◾ Water & Sewer included About Our Community: Pinebrook Apartments, where modern living meets unparalleled convenience. Nestled in a prime location near Rt. 50 and I-495, our community offers a gateway to seamless connectivity, ensuring you're just moments away from shopping, dining, and the vibrant energy of Washington, DC. Take a virtual tour through our photo gallery and envision a life of comfort and ease at Pinebrook Apartments. Your gateway to modern, convenient living awaits. Pet Policy: Pets - Max 2 allowed One time Fee $100.00, Rent $40.00, Cats - allowed Dogs - allowed Max weight 25 lb each, Wonderful Amenities: ◾ 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance ◾ Assigned Parking ◾ Blocks to Landover Metro - Orange Line ◾ Close to Rt. 50 and Northwest Stadium ◾ Co-mingled Recycling Offered ◾ Near Metro bus Service ◾ On-site Laundry Room Contact Information: Address: 2614 Pinebrook Ave. Landover, MD 20785 Call our office at show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=pinebrook&rp=tqgiXQ7nzdeM&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=pinebrook&rp=tqgiXQ7nzdeM&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=pinebrook&rp=tqgiXQ7nzdeM&t=trt All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY R7SH879MS6C7MRXE",
