        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Brookland Ridge Apartments 400 Taylor Street, NE Washington, DC 20017 Text or call for details at show contact info . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 2 BR - 1 BA - 939 sq ft Monthly Price: $2132 - $4050 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: Call . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . One Month Free Rent! Welcome to Brookland Ridge Apartments-where comfort lives alongside convenience in a peaceful setting. These modern apartments in Northeast, DC, offer the practical features and thoughtful touches that make a difference, from in-home washers and dryers to private balconies and oversized closets, in select units. Beyond your door, enjoy perks like a 24-hour fitness center, outdoor grilling spots, and easy on-site parking-all just minutes from city life. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: − Flexible Lease Terms − Grill − On-Site Parking − On-site Recycling − Picnic Area − Playground − Property Manager on Site − Public Transportation − Recycling − Walk-Up − 24- Hour Fitness Center with Free Weights − Caring and Award Winning Staff − Controlled-Access Buildings − Convenient to Downtown, Capitol Hill, Catholic University, Children's Hospital, Washington Medical Center &amp Union Station − Nearby Tennis Courts at Turkey Thicket Recreation − Professional and Attentive Maintenance Staff − Quiet Community in Wooded Setting − Serene Picnic &amp Grilling Area For Entertaining − Tranquil, Garden Style Living − Within Blocks of Brookland-CUA Metro . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment Home Comes With: − Cable Ready − Ceiling Fan − Dishwasher − High Speed Internet Access − Microwave − Oven − Range − Refrigerator − Smoke Free − Tile Floors − Ceramic Tile Floor − Fully Equipped Kitchens with Breakfast Nook − Gas or Electric Range − Generously Sized Floor Plans − Oversized Walk-In Closets in Select Homes − Plush Wall-To-Wall Carpeting − Pre-wired for Cable and High-Speed Internet Access − Private Balcony or Terrace − Resident Controlled Heat and Air Conditioning − Roommate Style Floorplans Available . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Text or call for details at -- show contact info -- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BrooklandRidgeApts Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=n9uxcju2HWxH&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=n9uxcju2HWxH&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=n9uxcju2HWxH&t=sch Pets: Pets - Max 2 allowed, - One time Fee $400.00 - Rent $50.00 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY KO93EHM49VD6V6G",
