        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Community Location: Keith Street/ 28th Avenue - Temple Hills, MD 20748 Monthly Price: $1285 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Details: 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 636 sq ft Leasing Options: 12-Month Reach out via phone: show contact info Apartment Amenities: Property Features: ◾ Cable-ready units with controlled access ◾ Elevator ◾ Pet-friendly environment ◾ Refreshing swimming pool for residents to enjoy ◾ Round-the-clock access to laundry facilities ◾ 24/7 on-site management and maintenance team for prompt assistance and emergency support ◾ Balconies offering outdoor space and fresh air ◾ Central heating and air conditioning for year-round comfort ◾ Elegant vinyl and hardwood flooring for a contemporary aesthetic ◾ Modern kitchens with a choice of black and stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher ◾ Spacious floor plans tailored for comfort and functionality Description: Welcome to Marlow Towers, your new home in the heart of Temple Hills, Maryland. At Marlow Towers we are committed to offering a comfortable, convenient, and high-quality living experience. Our thoughtfully designed apartments and community features ensure you feel right at home. At Marlow Towers we take pride in creating a living environment that supports your lifestyle and provides peace of mind. Welcome home. 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom 636 Sq Ft 1 bd, 1 ba | Available Now **Rents from $1,285-$1,475. Online application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=marlow&rp=h1cFizw5KiW4&t=ap Rental Terms Rent: $1,285 Application Fee: $25 Available Now Pets: Pet Friendly Reach out via phone: show contact info Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=marlow&rp=h1cFizw5KiW4&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=marlow&rp=h1cFizw5KiW4&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=marlow&rp=h1cFizw5KiW4&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY E01BGA0A743RTN",
