        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Parkview Towers Visit our community today! 7667 Maple Ave Takoma Park, MD 20912 Call us today at show contact info Monthly Price: $1450 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Type: 1-BR 1-BA Apartment Size: 700 sq ft Lease Terms: 12-Month Pet Policy: What you'll find in our community: − Affordable Housing − Controlled Access − Disability Access − Elevator − Emergency Maintenance − Free Onsite Parking − Laundry Facility − Onsite Maintenance − Onsite Management − Public Transportation − Easy Access to Shopping, Dining, Entertainment, I-495 − Explore the endless attractions nearby in the nation's capital − Freeway Access − Great outdoor entertainment − Housing Choice Vouchers Accepted − One Mile from Takoma Park Metro − Recycling Available − Shopping Nearby − Something for everyone: shops, restaurants, bars, art studios − Variety of annual festivals and events Description: Comfortable Living at an Affordable Price! The Takoma Park apartments at Parkview Towers offer great amenities and one of the best locations in the Maryland/DC area. Our roomy one, two and three bedroom apartment homes feature modern appliances, sunny windows, a formal dining room and expansive living room and bedrooms. All utilities are included in the rent and the community is located only one mile from the Takoma Park Metro and offers a bus stop at the property entrance. Residents also enjoy easy access to shopping, dining and I-495. This apartment comes with: − Closet space − Complete Appliance Package − Dishwasher − Elevator(s) − Formal Dining Room − Garbage Disposal − Large Apartment Floor Plans − Patio or Balcony − Refrigerator − Stove Call us today at show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=parkview_towers&rp=hHEwUgZMTXea&t=wb Income Restrictions for Parkview Towers # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $59,820       2 People   -   $68,340       3 People   -   $76,860       4 People   -   $85,380       5 People   -   $92,220       6 People   -   $99,060 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. Parkview Towers is an affordable housing community. INCOME RESTRICTIONS APPLY. Rent and income limits are based upon the number of occupants and median family income (MFI) (also known as area median income (AMI)) information from the U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development (HUD). INCOME RESTRICTIONS Family Composition - 60% AMI 1 person - $59,820 |2 persons - $68,340| 3 persons - $76,860 4 persons - $85,380| 5 persons - $92,220 |6 persons - $99,060 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2C0F915515D34BB8",
