        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Amherst Square 2315 Blueridge Ave #14 Wheaton, MD 20902 Call us at show contact info Apartment Information: 1 - 4 Bedroom | 1 - 1.5 Bath Apartment Size: 820 - 1300 sq ft Monthly Price: $1591 - $2500 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Includes: ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Central Air Conditioning ➢ Classic Refinished Wood Flooring ➢ Formal Dining Room ➢ Full Kitchen with Window ➢ Garbage Disposal ➢ High Speed Internet Available ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Storage and Closet Space Property Description: \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" Amherst Square apartments offer affordable living just outside of DC. The apartments are large and roomy, offer a formal dining room and a full kitchen with a window. There is plenty of storage and closet space and beautifully refinished wood flooring. Plus, residents don't have to go far to get anywhere with the Metro, bus and Wheaton Mall all within easy walking distance. It is easy to see why so many have chosen to make Amherst Square their home! Property Amenities: ➢ Community Center ➢ Easy access to I-495,I-270,I-95 ➢ Easy Access to Major Roadways ➢ Laundry Facility ➢ Playground ➢ Convenient to MARC commuter train ➢ Convenient to nearby Silver Spring, Takoma Park, and Washington D.C. ➢ Near Retail, Restaurants and Entertainment ➢ Walk to Wheaton Metro (Red Line) Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=amherst_square&rp=x3GyepC5Z3zd&t=wb Call us at show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: $25 monthly pet rent. $350 deposit per pet nonrefundable. Income Restrictions for Amherst Square # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $49,260       2 People   -   $56,280       3 People   -   $63,300       4 People   -   $70,320       5 People   -   $75,960       6 People   -   $81,600 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. Income Limits Apply - Please ask a Leasing Consultant for details. Minimum Income Requirements: 1 Bedroom - $37,740 2 Bedroom - $44,460 3 Bedroom - $50,430 4 Bedroom - $56,880 Application fee - $15 per adult member over the age of 18. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EA6A83B43D9647D1",
