        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Gardens of Gaithersburg Apartments Visit Our Community Today! 423 North Frederick Ave Gaithersburg, MD 20877 Contact us for more information! show contact info Income Restrictions Apply! Comfortable living can be yours at Gardens of Gaithersburg! Our small community in Gaithersburg features a community garden, play structures, onsite permit parking, and secured access buildings. Conveniently located near shopping, dining and entertainment, our community also has easy access to public transportation. Inside your apartment, you'll find updated kitchens, plenty of closet space, hardwood floors, and window coverings. An onsite laundry care center makes clothing care a breeze. Contact us today for a personal tour! Available NOW, apply today! *Special $1,599 move in by July 15th* Bedrooms: 1 | Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 700 sq ft Monthly Price: $1646 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Our Residents Enjoy: − Emergency Maintenance − Pet Friendly − Playground − Public Transportation − Recycling Available − Resident Controlled Entry − Se Habla Espanol − Section 8 Vouchers Accepted − Shopping Nearby − Smoke Free − Ask about our Income Restrictions! − Easy walking distance to shopping and dining − Laundry in each building − Ride-On Bus less than a block away This Apartment Home Comes With: − Central A/C and heating − Dishwasher − Dual Pane Windows − Electric Stove − Hardwood Flooring (in select units) − Linen Closet − Microwave − Mini Blinds − Refrigerator − Tile flooring (in kitchen and bath) Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ResidentialOneMD/ Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=gardens_of_gaithersburg&rp=8uqsbpfAxXJA&t=wb 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=gardens_of_gaithersburg&rp=8uqsbpfAxXJA&t=trt Contact us for more information! show contact info Pet-Policy: PETS WELCOME Please note that there is a specific breed and weight restrictions in place. Pet rent and deposit required Lease-Length: 12-Month Call for Directions INCOME RESTRICTIONS APPLY All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 381DC70C357A4EA3",
