orage with repair station ❖ Dog park and spa ❖ Dry cleaning lockers ❖ Next to the Waterfront Metro station ❖ Package acceptance ❖ Resident lounge ❖ Rooftop deck with grills and pool ❖ Shared workspace with printing ❖ Air conditioning ❖ Granite countertops ❖ Open-concept layout ❖ Plank flooring ❖ Stainless steel appliances ❖ Tile backsplash ❖ Washer and dryer in-home Pets: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. We also have a dog park and pet spa so your furry friends can live the good life too. Note we do have some restrictions please view our full pet policy below. We welcome cats and dogs!* Pet move-in fee: $500 Per dog monthly fee: $55 Per cat monthly fee: $55 *Maximum of two pets per apartment. Breed restrictions may apply. Business Hours: Tue - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 2:00 PM Ready to Lease? Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LexandLeoApartments Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=leo_at_waterfront_station&rp=mEWgikUf2pUb&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=leo_at_waterfront_station&rp=mEWgikUf2pUb&t=sch * Pricing, specials and availability are subject to change without notice and may be subject to specific lease terms and other conditions. Contact leasing associate for details. Bernstein Management Corporation will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person because the person will provide the rental payment, in whole or in part, through a voucher for rental housing assistance provided as applicable by the District, state, or federal government. Equal Housing Opportunity. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 47433F018AEE4D82",
