        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Leo at Waterfront Station, located at 1150 4th St SW Washington, DC 20024. Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Description ........ Enjoy a location within minutes of all the best D.C. has to offer when you make Leo at Waterfront Station your home! Our Southwest D.C. apartments are situated within walking or riding distance to everywhere you need and everything you want. We're pet-friendly, too! Bedrooms ........... 2 Bathrooms ......... 2 Sq Footage ......... 890 sq ft Monthly Price: $2956 - $3425 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Term ........ Variable Amenity List ...... ✓ Chic clubroom ✓ Conference room space ✓ Dog-washing boutique ✓ Fitness classes ✓ Heated infinity edge pool on roof deck ✓ Outdoor patio with gas grill and fireplace ✓ Party room with bar and kitchen ✓ Yoga and aerobics space ✓ Full-service concierge ✓ Game room with pool table and multiple TVs ✓ Nearby Capital Bikeshare and Zipcar stations ✓ Rooftop deck with incredible views of D.C. and Virginia ✓ Shared workspace and Wi-Fi lounge ✓ State-of-the-art fitness center with cardio and weightlifting machines ✓ Steps to the Waterfront Metro station on the Green Line ✓ Underground controlled access parking Apartment Home Features ..... ✓ Air Conditioning ✓ Ceiling Fan(s) ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Granite Countertop(s) ✓ Island Kitchens ✓ Microwave ✓ Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ Walk In Closet(s) ✓ Washer Dryer In Unit ✓ Floor-to-ceiling windows ✓ Frameless glass-enclosed showers ✓ Full-size energy efficient washer & dryer ✓ Moveable kitchen island with extra cabinets ✓ Remote operated bedroom ceiling fans Our Pet Policy ... We understand pets are a huge part of good living. Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. We also have a dog park and pet spa so your furry friends can live the good life too. Note we do have some restrictions please view our full pet policy below. We welcome cats and dogs!* Pet move-in fee: $500 Per dog monthly fee: $55 Per cat monthly fee: $55 *Maximum of two pets per apartment. Breed restrictions may apply. Leasing Hours ... Tue - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 2:00 PM Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Our Location ..... 1150 4th St SW Washington, DC 20024 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LexandLeoApartments Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=leo_at_waterfront_station&rp=7uFjKVWD2hn5&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=leo_at_waterfront_station&rp=7uFjKVWD2hn5&t=sch * Pricing, specials and availability are subject to change without notice and may be subject to specific lease terms and other conditions. Contact leasing associate for details. Bernstein Management Corporation will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person because the person will provide the rental payment, in whole or in part, through a voucher for rental housing assistance provided as applicable by the District, state, or federal government. Equal Housing Opportunity. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EE852D65EF964EC",
