        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Monthly Price: $1930 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 826 sq ft | BEDROOMS: 2 | BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 12-Month Call: show contact info ABOUT COMMUNITY: Our garden style community is located in highly sought after Silver Spring, MD. Pet Policy: Cats - allowed, Rent $50.00, Dogs - allowed, Rent $50.00, Restrictions: Breed Restrictions Apply APARTMENT FEATURES: ➢ Air Conditioner ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Disposal ➢ Heating ➢ Kitchen ➢ Large Closets ➢ Patio/Balcony ➢ Tub/Shower ➢ Vinyl Flooring ➢ Window Coverings COMMUNITY FEATURES: ➢ *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ➢ Availability 24 Hours ➢ Laundry Facilities ➢ Located next door to Nolte Park ➢ Off Street Parking ➢ On-Site Maintenance ➢ On-Site Management ➢ Public Transportation ➢ Report Rent and Build Credit with IDIQ ➢ Sports Courts CONTACT US TODAY! Parkside Terrace 506 Easley St Silver Spring, MD 20910 Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Wed: 11:00 AM - 5:30 PM Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Call: show contact info Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=parkside_terrace&rp=jdnAQuQisdMy&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=parkside_terrace&rp=jdnAQuQisdMy&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=parkside_terrace&rp=jdnAQuQisdMy&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=parkside_terrace&rp=jdnAQuQisdMy&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY C7D8DAA8A2F3482",
