        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Quebec Arms Apartments Monthly Price: $1575 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 683 sq ft BEDROOMS: 1 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 12-Month Call: show contact info One Month Free APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: ✓ Beautiful hardwood floors, some carpeted apartment homes ✓ Garbage Disposal ✓ Generous room sizes ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Individually controlled heating and air conditioning ✓ Mini blinds in all windows ✓ One, two, and three bedroom apartment homes ✓ Spacious Closets Quebec Arms offers spacious interiors with plenty of charm. You're certain to find the right home to fit your lifestyle. Our one, two, and three-bedroom apartment homes have the amenities and location you desire. In addition to a variety of planned activities, residents enjoy a playground, central laundry facility, on-site shuttle bus service to the University of Maryland and much more. Ideally located, Quebec Arms is close to top employers, plenty of entertainment, shopping, and dining, and easy access to downtown Silver Spring, Washington, D.C., minutes from the Green Line Metro plus easy access to I-495, Baltimore Washington Parkway, and US Rte. 1. We are steps away from the Prince Georges Plaza and The Mall at Prince Georges. Our location offers convenient access to the best shopping, dining, and entertainment Hyattsville, MD has to offer. At Quebec Arms, you'll find the perfect combination of comfort and value. Experience the perfect balance of space and accessibility in this oversized one-bedroom apartment at Quebec Arms. Unlike the cramped new builds in the area, our floor plans are designed with real living in mind, featuring a sprawling living room that easily fits a full furniture set and a dedicated dining area for home-cooked meals. You will love the massive walk-in closets that provide all the storage you have been looking for and the large windows that flood the space with natural light. Our location is a commuter's dream, situated just a short trip from the West Hyattsville Metro station and the vibrant Arts District. Whether you are heading to UMD or downtown DC, getting around is effortless with easy access to major transit and the Northwest Branch Trail. Hablamos Espanol. Our professional on-site management team is dedicated to providing excellent service, and we are proud to offer full bilingual support as we speak Spanish. Come tour your new home today and see why Quebec Arms is the hidden gem of Hyattsville. Income guidelines apply. Qualification is based on household size and verified income. Please contact the leasing office for details PROPERTY FEATURES: ✓ 1 block to Metro ✓ Controlled Access ✓ On-site management ✓ Playground ✓ Some Paid Utilities ✓ Central laundry facility ✓ Close to Downtown Silver Spring and DC ✓ On-site Maintenance ✓ Shuttlebus service to University of MD ✓ Walking distance to shopping center PET POLICY: No pets allowed; VISIT US TODAY! 1400 Merrimac Dr Hyattsville, MD 20783 Call: show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=qDsPheMqtzow&t=wb 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=qDsPheMqtzow&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=qDsPheMqtzow&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 81BF749197D248D",
