        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Berkdale Apartments 661 Dulles Park Ct Herndon, VA 20170 Contact Info: show contact info SUMMER SAVINGS! Limited-Time Leasing Special Enjoy $1,500 Off Select Apartment Homes When You Move-In By 7/7/26! *Other restrictions may apply. Contact the leasing office for more details. Apartment Information: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bath Apartment Size: 593 sq ft Monthly Price: $1799 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Includes: ◾ Air Conditioner ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Garbage Disposal ◾ Large Closets ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Cable and High-Speed Internet Available ◾ Hardwood-Like Flooring ◾ Modern Kitchen Appliances ◾ Renovated Apartments ◾ Wall-To-Wall Carpet Property Description: I. ON-SITE MANAGEMENT Full time professional on-site staff available 7 days a week for all your needs. II.ON-SITE MAINTENANCE Have peace of mind with our 24-hour emergency maintenance team. III.NEIGHBORHOOD PERKS Easy access to nearly shopping and dining at Reston Town Center and Historic Herndon. IV.PET-FRIENDLY Dogs and cats are welcome here. Each home may have up to 2 fluffy friends. pet fees and pet rent may vary. Property Amenities: ◾ BBQ/Picnic Area ◾ Bilingual Staff ◾ Business Center ◾ Fairfax County Park - Next Door ◾ High Speed Internet ◾ On-Site Maintenance ◾ On-Site Management ◾ Package Receiving ◾ Reserved Parking Space ◾ Storage Space ◾ *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ◾ Bike Trail, Nearby Shopping and Restaurants ◾ Close to VA-267 (Dulles Toll Road) Connecting to I-66 and I-495, As Well As Rt 28 and Dulles Greenway ◾ Flexible Rent Payment Options with FLEX ◾ Laundry Facilities in Each Building ◾ Park-Like Setting - Manicured Landscaping ◾ Pre-installed WiFi with 1 Month Free from Cox ◾ Report Rent and Build Credit with IDIQ ◾ Short-term leases are available - 2 to 12 Month Lease Lengths ◾ Walking Distance to 2 Grocery Stores Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=berkdale&rp=6b5KGx6gkTC8&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=berkdale&rp=6b5KGx6gkTC8&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=berkdale&rp=6b5KGx6gkTC8&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=berkdale&rp=6b5KGx6gkTC8&t=sch Contact Info: show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Wed: 11:00 AM - 5:30 PM Thu - Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: Cats - 2 allowed, One time Fee $500.00, Rent $35.00, Dogs - 2 allowed, One time Fee $500.00, Rent $60.00, Restrictions: Breed Restrictions Apply All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY BC3992A99ED347",
