        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 32-Thirtytwo, located at 3232 Georgia Avenue NW Washington, DC 20010. Call us for more information! show contact info Description ........ Enjoy an unrivaled NORTHWEST DC apartment living experience just minutes from the Metro in the heart of the Parkview/Columbia Heights neighborhood. Bedrooms ........... 1 Bathrooms ......... 1 Sq Footage ......... 722 sq ft Monthly Price: $1600 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Term ........ 12-Month Amenity List ...... − Affordable Housing − Built Green − Courtyard − Emergency Maintenance − Income Restrictions Apply − Onsite Maintenance − Onsite Management − Roof Top Deck − Bus stop at building entrance − Community lounge with wifi − Convenient location to Columbia Heights − Minutes to the Georgia Ave/Petworth Metro − State of the art laundry facility Apartment Home Features ..... − Central Heat and Air − High Ceilings − Oversized Closet(s) − Stainless Steel Appliances − Upgraded Cabinetry − Window Coverings − Wood Like Flooring − 9 foot ceilings − Ample closet and storage space − Black laminate counters − Designer kitchens − Energy efficient appliances and windows − Faux wood flooring − Pecan colored maple cabinets Our Pet Policy ... No pets allowed Leasing Hours ... Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call us for more information! show contact info Our Location ..... 3232 Georgia Avenue NW Washington, DC 20010 Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=32-thirtytwo&rp=eXrCUV3WJPT8&t=wb Income Restrictions for 32-Thirtytwo # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $64,980       2 People   -   $74,280       3 People   -   $83,580       4 People   -   $92,820       5 People   -   $100,260 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 575FADDF17134E0",
