        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Lex at Waterfront Station Address: 1151 4th Street SW Washington, DC 20024 Monthly Price: $2100 - $3194 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: Efficiency | Baths: 1 | Sq. Footage: 396 sq ft | Terms: Variable Call our office at show contact info + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ❖ Air Conditioning ❖ Hardwood Floor ❖ High Ceilings in select units ❖ Stainless Steel Appliances ❖ Walk In Closet(s) ❖ Floor-to-ceiling windows ❖ Frameless glass-enclosed showers ❖ Full-size energy efficient washer & dryer ❖ Granite countertops with subway tile backsplash ❖ Moveable kitchen island with extra cabinets ❖ Open pocket doors ❖ Remote operated bedroom ceiling fans + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ❖ 24/7 concierge ❖ 24/7 emergency maintenance ❖ 24/7 fitness center with studio ❖ Controlled access ❖ Courtyard with grills ❖ Garage parking ❖ On-site management ❖ Package acceptance ❖ Resident lounge and game room ❖ Rooftop deck with pool and grills ❖ Shared workspace with printing ❖ Nearby Capital Bikeshare and Zipcar ❖ Next to the Waterfront Metro station + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: The Lex at Waterfront Station apartment community offers some of the best Southwest Waterfront apartments in DC. Our apartment homes are available in efficiency, one, and two bedroom configurations for a home and lifestyle perfectly suited to your needs. Penthouse apartment homes are also available and include coffee service, high ceilings, Nest® thermostats, Rain shower heads, and private access. Whether it's a small intimate space or a large spacious residence, the Lex at Waterfront Station has a home ready for you. Pets: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. We also have a dog park and pet spa so your furry friends can live the good life too. Pet Move-in Fee - $500. $55 Monthly Fee Per Pet Maximum of two pets per apartment. Breed restrictions may apply. Call our office at show contact info Hours: Tue - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 2:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LexandLeoApartments Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=viak7CCy7chh&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=viak7CCy7chh&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=viak7CCy7chh&t=sch Bernstein Management Corporation will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person if the rental payment, whole or part, will be provided through a voucher for rent housing assistance from the District, state or federal government. Rental rates and availability are subject to change. Equal Housing Opportunity. Specials and availability are subject to change without notice. Restrictions apply. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY AXI4RHH7N14IXNE8",
