 information: Call us today! show contact info Terms: 12-Month Pets: Max 2 Allowed | One time Fee $250 | Rent $25 Restrictions: Breed Restrictions Apply Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=5ygPUtJwVFLJ&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=5ygPUtJwVFLJ&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 8FEB5DC7C5EF4F3",
