        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post The Benjamin at Landover Hills 4085 Warner Ave Landover Hills, MD 20784 Call for details: show contact info Apartment Information: 3 Bedroom | 1.5 Bath Apartment Size: 1075 sq ft Monthly Price: $1969 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Includes: ◾ Breakfast Bar ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Freezer ◾ Gas Range ◾ Granite Countertops in Selected Units ◾ Huge Patio/Balcony ◾ Luxury Vinyl Tile Flooring in select apartments* ◾ Modern Cabinetry Available ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Renovated Kitchens & Bathrooms in select apartments* ◾ Vinyl Flooring in selected units ◾ Walk-In Closets in selected units ◾ Wall-to-Wall Carpeting in select apartments* Property Description: Leisure becomes second nature; our Olympic-sized pool and picnic area make sunny days feel brighter. And when you have a moment to spare, check out our other on-site amenities, including the playground, dog park, fitness center, and laundry facilities. These are only a glimpse into the exhilarating adventures The Benjamin enables. Reach out today to find out more! Property Amenities: ◾ *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ◾ 24/7 on Call Maintenance ◾ BBQ/Picnic Area ◾ Clubhouse ◾ Dog Park ◾ Fitness Center ◾ Laundry Facilities ◾ Olympic Sized Pool ◾ On-Site Laundry Facilities ◾ Playground ◾ Reserved Parking ◾ Sparkling Swimming Pool Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=benjamin_at_landover_hills&rp=dEg8fqayPRQ6&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=benjamin_at_landover_hills&rp=dEg8fqayPRQ6&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=benjamin_at_landover_hills&rp=dEg8fqayPRQ6&t=trt Call for details: show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Wed: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Thu - Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: We are pet-friendly! We welcome up to 2 pets per household. Breed restrictions apply. Please contact our leasing office for more details. - Type: Cats and Dogs - Max Number of Pets: 2 - No weight restriction 40 LBS - Pet deposit fee max: $300 for 1, $500 total for 2 - Pet monthly rent: $30 for cats and $50 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 392NCD68D7O7A80T",
