        "geocode_query": "2 Elmira St SE near South Capitol St SE",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1390 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Crescent Park Village: 2 Elmira St SE Washington, DC 20032 Apartment for Rent: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 710 sq ft | Lease Length: 12-Month Phone: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ● Bike friendly ● Highways Nearby ● Laundry Facilities ● Near Downtown ● On-site parking ● Parks Nearby ● Playground ● Well lit streets ● Availability 24 Hours ● Controlled Access/Gated ● Easy street parking ● Heavy Car Traffic Area ● Older/Historical Building ● On-Site Management & Maintenance ● Pay Your Rent Online ● Public Transportation Nearby ● Sidewalk Lined Streets ● Tree Lined Streets APARTMENT AMENITIES ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Crescent Park Village offers the full package featuring renovated kitchens, free basic cable, laundry rooms, 24-hour emergency maintenance services, and the ability to pay rent online from the comfort of your home. Located in the up and coming neighborhood of Congress Heights, Crescent Park Village Apartments offers comfortable one and two bedroom apartment homes. Welcome home! Pet Policy: Call for information Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=crescent_park_village&rp=fbaxChJzXdiD&t=wb Phone: show contact info Floor plan measurements are approximate and are for illustrative purposes only. While we do not doubt the floor plan's accuracy, we make no guarantee, warranty or representation as to the accuracy and completeness of the floor plan. You and or your advisers should conduct a careful, independent investigation of the property to determine to your satisfaction as to the suitability of the property for your space requirements. Income restrictions apply. Please call for more details. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A85472E89C72459",
