        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Apply to receive one month free* Offer only eligible up to 48-hours after touring! Welcome to Towns at Andrew's Park Beds: 3 Baths: 2.5 Square Feet: 2400 More unit details at: https://avenue5.aptfeatures.com/4tdj7k Move to a Stunning Camp Springs Rental Community Call Now - show contact info x 221 OR Text 221 to show contact info to text with us.   Community Info Newly designed in an incredible location, your new Camp Springs rental home near Andrews Airforce Base lets residents experience a true hidden gem. Enjoy a warm, neighborhood feel in an ideal location right off I-495. Our three and four-bedroom townhomes are thoughtfully appointed with elevated finishes and amenities designed to provide comfort and a sense of home. Residence Features ✩  Beautiful Wood Flooring ✩  New Townhomes ✩  Private Two-Car Garage ✩  Washer and Dryer In-Unit ✩  Open Concept Living ✩  Private Balconies ✩  Powder Room ✩  High End Finishes ✩  A Must See ✩  Walk-In Closets ✩  Granite Countertops ✩  Top Line Stainless Appliances ✩  Expansive 2400 sqf ✩  Large Kitchen Islands ✩  Eat-In Kitchen ✩  Double Vanities Community Features ✩  Tour Today ✩  One Mile from Joint Base Andrews ✩  Playground ✩  Onsite Retail: Dominos, Advanced Auto Parts, & Wawa ✩  Bus Stop Located Directly Outside Community ✩  Prime Location Right off I-495 ✩  Short Distance to Branch Avenue Metro Station Pet Policy Pets Allowed Finding a pet friendly apartment can be difficult at times. We know how much you love your furry friends, and we are pleased to welcome four-legged residents to Towns at Andrews Park. We love your pets as much as you do. Please speak with an associate for more details. Office Hours Tuesday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity YOaA5dja",
