        "locality": "Woodbridge",
        "geocode_query": "16573 Nanticoke Way, Woodbridge",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Approximately 1107 Sq. Ft. Interested In This Unit? Use this link for more details: https://Fairfield-apts.com/3knuld Call Now - show contact info x 68 OR Text 68 to show contact info to text our team. Three Great Options For Affordable Living In Woodbridge, VA Community Info: Conveniently located in Prince William County, Riverwoods Apartments, Riverwoods at Towne Square Apartments and Riverwoods at Lake Ridge Apartments in Woodbridge, VA are three different communities offering affordable living with a bounty of conveniences. These 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartments and townhomes include a modern kitchen, in-home washer and dryer, and community amenities that expand your living space. Take a dip in the pool, break a sweat in the fitness center, or stroll with Fido around the beautifully landscaped grounds and nearby trails. No matter which Riverwoods community you call home, there are plenty of perks to enjoy. We are pleased to offer affordable living options — Income limits apply . Call us or visit us today! Our leasing office is located at Riverwoods Apartments and will happily assist with questions about each of these three affordable Woodbridge communities. Features: ‣  Fully Equipped Kitchen Including A Disposal And Dishwasher ‣  Wood-Look Flooring In Kitchen And Bathroom ‣  Kitchen Pantry ‣  Air Conditioning ‣  Kitchen Island With Breakfast Bar ‣  Oversized Closet ‣  Breakfast Bar ‣  Pet Friendly - Puppies And Kittens Welcome (Breed Restrictions Apply) ‣  Ceiling Fan ‣  Tons Of Natural Light ‣  In-Home Washer And Dryer Community Amenities: ‣  Proximity To I-95 And Rte. 1 ‣  Proximity To Potomac Mills Mall, Medical Services, Quantico Base, And Fort Belvoir ‣  Picnic And BBQ Area ‣  Pool With Spacious Sun Deck ‣  Garage Parking At Select Communities ‣  On-Site Management ‣  Minutes To The River Oaks Shopping Center ‣  Public Transportation ‣  Ample Parking ‣  Fitness Center ‣  Playground ‣  On-Site Maintenance ‣  Children's Wading Pool ‣  Clubhouse Pet Policy: Dogs and cats, including puppies and kittens under 1 year old, are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check and shots by 6 months of age. A signed animal addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. $500 deposit per pet $50/month per pets Income Requirements: Current Income Limits 1 person: $63,300 2 people: $72,360 3 people: $81,420 4 people: $90,420 5 people: $97,680 6 people: $104,940 7 people: $112,140 Office Hours: Monday-Tuesday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Wednesday: 11:00AM-5:00PM Thursday-Friday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Riverwoods Apartments, Riverwoods at Lake Ridge Apartments & Riverwoods at Towne Square Townhomes 16573 Nanticoke Way, Woodbridge, VA, 22191 Photos on this ad may not reflect all floorplans. Advertised pricing and availability are subject to change without notice and cannot be guaranteed. Equal Housing Opportunity 0ZgqXqrrAO",
