        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a Studio , 1 Bath, Approximately 380 Sq. Ft. More unit details at: https://Laramar.aptrentnow.com/sztdsa Call Now - show contact info x 193 OR Text 193 to show contact info to text our team directly. MODERN STYLE. BREATHTAKING VIEWS. Community Info: Experience modern, renovated apartment homes at Bridgeyard Apartments, located in the heart of Old Town Alexandria. Enjoy extraordinary waterfront views of the Potomac River and easy access to I-95/495 for a stress-free commute. Our studio, one, and two-bedroom apartments feature double-paned windows, wood flooring in select units, stylish Lido cabinetry, granite countertops, and energy-efficient appliances, including built-in microwaves. Stay fit with our expansive fitness center and welcome guests with the Butterfly MX smartphone intercom system. Plus, the Mount Vernon Trail is just steps away, offering 18 miles of multi-use recreation trails for walking, running, or biking. Contact us today to schedule a tour! Features: ‣  Dishwasher ‣  Window Coverings ‣  Stainless Steel Appliances* ‣  Microwave ‣  Refrigerator with Icemaker ‣  Ceramic Kitchen Tile ‣  Lido Style Cabinetry ‣  Granite Countertops* ‣  Serene River Views* ‣  Air Conditioner ‣  Patio/Balcony ‣  Chic Two-Panel Interior Doors ‣  Cable Ready ‣  9 Ft Ceilings ‣  Ceiling Fan ‣  Carpeting ‣  Hardwood Floors* ‣  Gas Range Community Amenities: ‣  ButterflyMX Guest Entry Access ‣  On-Site Management ‣  Elevator ‣  Fetch Package Delivery Service ‣  Selected ‣  Laundry Facilities ‣  Spanish Speaking Staff ‣  Courtyard ‣  Walk to Old Town Shops and Restaurants ‣  Directly on Mt. Vernon Paved Bike/Hike Trail ‣  Easy Access to Huntington, Eisenhower Ave, and King St. Metro Stations ‣  Off Street Parking ‣  Waterfront BBQ and Picnic Area ‣  Beautiful Potomac River Views ‣  Ample Parking Including Garage Options ‣  Public Transportation ‣  Fitness Center ‣  Sitting area with fire pit ‣  Swimming Pool right on the 