        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Cozy Clean Condo - Available Soon! 9851 Hellingly Place, Gaithersburg, MD 20886 1630.00 / Month 1 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6Njk2MTc4?property=1320301&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/9851-hellingly-place-gaithersburg-md/4bab7537-5f9c-4ee8-8022-3a256f7238b4?source=craigslist Property Description: Immaculate studio tailored to the needs of the traveling professional. Freshly painted. Designed for comfort and convenience. Open floor plan provides a sense of airiness/freedom. Blend of rustic, modern decor creates an ambiance of relaxation. Memory foam bed with soft linens and comfortable pillows provide restful sleep. Thoughtfully appointed work desk/chair for focused productivity. Fully equipped kitchenette with stainless steel appliances, granite counter, and modern black sink. Dining table folds out for any culinary creations. Bathroom is a sanctuary of cleanliness/serenity with jetted tub for pampering yourself. New stackable washer/dryer next to the bedroom. Easy access to nearby hospitals, medical centers, and professional offices. Walking distance to local bus stop and 12 min drive to Shady Grove Metro. Less than a mile from stores, library, Dunkin Donuts, and Costco. Multiple parks within 2 miles. Access to major commuter routes. Parking included. Property Type : Condo Pets : No Pets Allowed Smoking : NO Lease Term : 1630.00 / Month 1600.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 08/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: 2 People Utilities Included : Appliances : Refrigerator Dryer Microwave Washer Freezer Range Oven Amenities : Cable Ready On Site Laundry Swimming Pool Furnished Wired For Internet Heating & Cooling : Forced Air Heatpump Central Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6Njk2MTc4?property=1320301&source=cl Have questions? Contact t