        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 1347 Sq. Ft. Want more info on this unit? See the link (below): https://lerner.aptsup.com/0ynhnm Call Now - show contact info x 132 OR Text 132 to show contact info to text us. Live better then ever at our beautifully wooded community in Greenbelt, Maryland. Community Info: Surrounded by acres of green space with mature landscaping and tall shade trees, Lerner University Square is a hidden gem in Greenbelt, Maryland. As a resident, you will have exclusive access to community amenities, such as a sparkling swimming pool, basketball court, and playground. Inside the apartments, you'll enjoy fully equipped kitchens, completely renovated with granite countertops and maple cabinets, and all apartments include a washer and dryer. With nearby access to the Greenbelt Metro/MARC and New Carrollton Metro/Amtrak Station and easy access to I-95 and the Capital Beltway, getting around town has never been so easy. If that weren't enough, we also have metro bus stops and a University of Maryland shuttle stop located within the community to take you to University of Maryland and other nearby shopping and dining destinations. Lerner University Square is the only community you should consider calling \"home\". Features: ‣  Modern Appliances ‣  Eat-In Kitchens in Most Apartments ‣  Renovated Apartment Homes ‣  Spacious Floor Plans ‣  Pantry Cabinets ‣  Oversized, Private Balconies and Patios ‣  Equipped Kitchens ‣  Walk-In Closets in All Apartments ‣  In-Home Washers and Dryers Community Amenities: ‣  Pet-Friendly ‣  Sparkling Swimming Pool ‣  Plentiful, Free Parking ‣  Basketball Court ‣  Playground ‣  Convenient Location ‣  Fitness Center ‣  Resident-Exclusive Events ‣  Controlled Access Buildings ‣  24/7 Maintenance ‣  Nearby Entertainment Pet Policy: Fee: $350 Rent: $50 Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM University Square 157 Westway Road, Greenbelt, MD, 20770 Equal Housing Opportunity SkJa8GjR97Qt",
