        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Brookland Ridge Apartments 400 Taylor Street, NE Washington, DC 20017 Monthly Price: $2047 - $4099 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 1.5 Square Footage: 972 sq ft Call or text for details at show contact info Features in this apartment home: ❖ Dishwasher ❖ Disposal ❖ High Speed Internet Access ❖ Microwave ❖ Oven ❖ Range ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Smoke Free ❖ Tile Floors ❖ Window Coverings ❖ Ceramic Tile Floor ❖ Full Size Washer/Dryer in Every Apartment Home ❖ Fully Equipped Kitchens with Breakfast Nook ❖ Gas or Electric Range ❖ Generously Sized Floor Plans ❖ Plush Wall-To-Wall Carpeting ❖ Pre-wired for Cable and High-Speed Internet Access ❖ Private Balcony or Terrace ❖ Resident Controlled Heat and Air Conditioning ❖ Roommate Style Floorplans Available About the community: One Month Free Rent! Each layout is built with your needs in mind-generous closets, flexible designs, and warm finishes set the tone for easy, comfortable living. Whether you're staying in or stepping out, your space supports every part of your routine. Check out our Floor Plans page to find out all the details! Amenities at our property: ❖ Flexible Lease Terms ❖ Grill ❖ On-Site Parking ❖ On-site Recycling ❖ Picnic Area ❖ Playground ❖ Property Manager on Site ❖ Public Transportation ❖ Recycling ❖ Walk-Up ❖ 24- Hour Fitness Center with Free Weights ❖ Caring and Award Winning Staff ❖ Controlled-Access Buildings ❖ Convenient to Downtown, Capitol Hill, Catholic University, Children's Hospital, Washington Medical Center &amp Union Station ❖ Nearby Tennis Courts at Turkey Thicket Recreation ❖ Professional and Attentive Maintenance Staff ❖ Quiet Community in Wooded Setting ❖ Serene Picnic &amp Grilling Area For Entertaining ❖ Tranquil, Garden Style Living ❖ Within Blocks of Brookland-CUA Metro Additional information: Call or text for details at show contact info Terms: Call Pets: Pets - Max 2 allowed, - One time Fee $400.00 - Rent $50.00 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BrooklandRidgeApts Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=htPXaK6PaEGn&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=htPXaK6PaEGn&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=brookland_ridge&rp=htPXaK6PaEGn&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 86S162J4ZA2JO4C",
