        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1920 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Gardens of Gaithersburg Apartments: 423 North Frederick Ave Gaithersburg, MD 20877 Apartment for Rent: 2-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 900 sq ft | Lease Length: 12-Month Office Phone: show contact info *Special $1,899 move in by July 20th* PROPERTY AMENITIES ◾ Community Garden ◾ Community Laundry Room ◾ Emergency Maintenance ◾ Guest Parking ◾ Income Restrictions Apply ◾ Pet Friendly ◾ Playground ◾ Recycling Available ◾ Section 8 Vouchers Accepted ◾ Shopping Nearby ◾ Ask about our Income Restrictions! ◾ Easy walking distance to shopping and dining ◾ Laundry in each building ◾ Ride-On Bus less than a block away APARTMENT AMENITIES ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Ceiling Fans ◾ Central A/C and heating ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Dual Pane Windows ◾ Hardwood Flooring (in select units) ◾ Linen Closet ◾ Microwave ◾ Spacious living room/dining room ◾ Tile flooring (in kitchen and bath) ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Income Restrictions Apply! Located just off North Frederick Avenue in Gaithersburg, this small community is a hidden gem. Generous floorplans include beautiful, updated kitchens, ample closets, hardwood flooring (in select apartments). Every apartment home has complementary window treatments and each apartment home is located within steps of a laundry facility. Residents have use of a community garden, and playgrounds. The apartments are all located within resident controlled access buildings and free parking is by permit only. The North Frederick Avenue location places dining, shopping and entertainment all within easy reach and, for convenience, there is access to public transportation. Pet Policy: PETS WELCOME Please note that there is a specific breed and weight restrictions in place. Pet rent and deposit required Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ResidentialOneMD/ Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=gardens_of_gaithersburg&rp=m11CWz1ypABv&t=wb Office Phone: show contact info INCOME RESTRICTIONS APPLY All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 00FE8FCB80484B0",
