        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - Berkdale Apartments! Address: 661 Dulles Park Ct Herndon, VA 20170 Contact us for more information! show contact info Beds: 3 / Baths: 1 / Size: 806 sq ft Monthly Price: $2395 - $2599 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. At Berkdale, you are just minutes from the Dulles Toll Road, Dulles Greenway, Herndon Parkway and Route 28/ (V-267) for quick access to transportation routes east toward DC and west toward Dulles International Airport as well as Loudoun County. In addition to our great location, you'll love our beautifully designed apartment homes with great features such as, spacious living/dining rooms, modern kitchens, walk-in closets, and included utilities (gas only). Enjoy park-like views from sundrenched windows! At Berkdale Apartments you can take a leisurely stroll to the Alabama Drive Park (a Fairfax County Park) next door, enjoy the community playground with your family and put your cooking skills to work at our grilling areas. We also offer short-term leases. Deposit: Call Length of Lease: 12-Month SUMMER SAVINGS! Limited-Time Leasing Special Enjoy $1,500 Off Select Apartment Homes When You Move-In By 7/7/26! *Other restrictions may apply. Contact the leasing office for more details. Property Features: ● BBQ/Picnic Area ● Business Center ● Fairfax County Park - Next Door ● High Speed Internet ● On-Site Maintenance ● On-Site Management ● Package Receiving ● Playground ● Reserved Parking Space ● Storage Space ● *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ● Bike Trail, Nearby Shopping and Restaurants ● Close to VA-267 (Dulles Toll Road) Connecting to I-66 and I-495, As Well As Rt 28 and Dulles Greenway ● Flexible Rent Payment Options with FLEX ● Laundry Facilities in Each Building ● Park-Like Setting - Manicured Landscaping ● Pre-installed WiFi with 1 Month Free from Cox ● Report Rent and Build Credit with IDIQ ● Short-term leases are available - 2 to 12 Month Lease Lengths ● Walking Distance to 2 Grocery Stores Apartment Amenities: ● Air Conditioner ● Dishwasher ● Garbage Disposal ● Large Closets ● Refrigerator ● Cable and High-Speed Internet Available ● Hardwood-Like Flooring ● Modern Kitchen Appliances ● Renovated Apartments ● Wall-To-Wall Carpet Pets: Cats - 2 allowed, One time Fee $500.00, Rent $35.00, Dogs - 2 allowed, One time Fee $500.00, Rent $60.00, Restrictions: Breed Restrictions Apply Business Hours: Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Wed: 11:00 AM - 5:30 PM Thu - Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 5:00 PM Ready to Lease? Contact us for more information! show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=berkdale&rp=xdUq6j2bbRNo&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=berkdale&rp=xdUq6j2bbRNo&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=berkdale&rp=xdUq6j2bbRNo&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 9EC7CED1334A45FA",
