        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Base monthly rent: $1397 Total Monthly Price: $1397 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Lex at Waterfront Station: 1151 4th Street SW Washington, DC 20024 Apartment for Rent: Efficiency-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 395 sq ft | Lease Length: Variable Phone Number: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ❖ 24/7 concierge ❖ 24/7 emergency maintenance ❖ 24/7 fitness center with studio ❖ Controlled access ❖ Courtyard with grills ❖ Garage parking ❖ On-site management ❖ Package acceptance ❖ Resident lounge and game room ❖ Rooftop deck with pool and grills ❖ Shared workspace with printing ❖ Nearby Capital Bikeshare and Zipcar ❖ Next to the Waterfront Metro station APARTMENT AMENITIES ❖ 24/7 concierge ❖ 24/7 fitness center with studio ❖ Attached garage parking ❖ Bike storage with repair station ❖ Courtyard with grills ❖ Dog park and spa ❖ Dry cleaning lockers ❖ Next to the Waterfront Metro station ❖ Package acceptance ❖ Resident lounge ❖ Rooftop deck with grills and pool ❖ Shared workspace with printing ❖ Air conditioning ❖ Appliances Included ❖ Open-concept layout ❖ Tile backsplash ❖ Washer and dryer in-home ADDITIONAL INFO Description: The vibrant Washington, D.C. area offers a wonderful array of activities and entertainment, and our Southwest Waterfront apartments put you close to all of the action. With easy access to upscale dining, local shopping and D.C.'s world-famous museums and monuments, you'll always have quick and convenient access to all of your favorite attractions. Transportation is a breeze at Lex at Waterfront Station! Located just outside of the Waterfront Station on the Green Line, you'll have easy access to public transportation. At our D.C. apartments for rent, we also feature community bike racks and offer garage parking to assure commuting is a breeze for all of our residents. No matter where you choose to work or play, our luxury Southwest Washington D.C. apartments are located to offer you easy access to everything you enjoy. Household income must be verified to match property income restrictions. Two most recent tax returns, six most recent bank statements for all accessible bank accounts and proof of all additional income is required (i.e. self-employment, recurring gifts, social security). If needed, other documentation may be requested. Pet Policy: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. Lex & Leo at Waterfront Station welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. We also have a dog park and pet spa so your furry friends can live the good life too. Pet Move-in Fee - $500. $55 Monthly Fee Per Pet Maximum of two pets per apartment. Breed restrictions may apply. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LexandLeoApartments Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=3AuYnsSD6ZxR&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=lex_at_waterfront_station&rp=3AuYnsSD6ZxR&t=sch Phone Number: show contact info Bernstein Management Corporation will not refuse to rent a rental unit to a person if the rental payment, whole or part, will be provided through a voucher for rent housing assistance from the District, state or federal government. Rental rates and availability are subject to change. Equal Housing Opportunity. Specials and availability are subject to change without notice. Restrictions apply. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 89F7BCFD97ED442",
