        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post -- The Shay -- Call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Monthly Price: $2225 - $3277 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bathroom Square Footage: 759 sq ft Welcome to The Shay, an apartment community designed for modern, vibrant living in Shaw - Washington, D.C.'s most exciting neighborhood. Just a few blocks from legendary venues like 9:30 Club and Howard Theatre, The Shay is surrounded by a neighborhood imbued with music, culture, and art. From inspired shopping and bustling nightlife to top-notch restaurants and live music, these sleek and stylish apartment residences are surrounded by DC's best boutique bodegas, coffee shops, brewpubs, bars, and more. With the excitement of 9th Street and U Street just a short walk away, life at The Shay is truly where culture meets cool. Lease now and live in the best new apartments in Shaw DC. Pet Policy: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. The Shay welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. Note we do have some restrictions please view our full pet policy below. Max 2 Allowed. One-time Fee: $500. Rent: $60 Per Pet. Restrictions: Breed Restrictions Check out our beautiful community featuring: ◾ 24 Hour Availability ◾ Breakfast/Coffee Concierge ◾ Controlled Access for Residents Only ◾ Covered Parking ◾ High Speed WiFi in Common Areas ◾ Maintenance On-Site ◾ On-Site Management Dedicated to Service Excellence ◾ Package Receiving ◾ Recycling ◾ Smoke-Free ◾ 24-hour Fitness Center with Free Weights ◾ Beautiful Lobby and High Speed Elevators ◾ Game Area with Billiards, Foosball, and More ◾ Incredible Access to Shopping, Cafes, Dining, and Retail right downstairs ◾ Landscaped Rooftop Deck with Plush Seating ◾ Monumental Views ◾ On-Site Retail ◾ Outdoor Patio with Grills and Kitchens ◾ Reflecting Pool ◾ Sparkling Pool with Lounge Chairs and Umbrellas Apartment features include: ◾ Built in Pantry Cabinet ◾ Central Heat and Air Conditioning ◾ Ideal Work from Home Layouts ◾ Oversized Stainless Steel Smart Appliances ◾ Slip Grip Tubs ◾ Spacious 10 foot ceilings ◾ Studio, Loft, One- to 2 Bedroom Plus Den Floorplans ◾ Terraced Patio/Balconies with select floorplans ◾ Beautiful Hardwood Flooring Throughout ◾ Custom Kitchen Cabinetry with Quartz Countertops ◾ Floor to Ceiling Windows ◾ Full-Sized, Stacked, In-unit Washer and Dryer ◾ Incredible DC Skyline Views ◾ Moveable Kitchen Islands in Select Apartment Homes ◾ Porcelain Matte Finished Bathroom Tile ◾ Rain Shower Heads Call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Tue - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sun: 10:00 AM - 3:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/theshaydc Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=shay&rp=oGTB43JnjFMj&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=shay&rp=oGTB43JnjFMj&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=shay&rp=oGTB43JnjFMj&t=sch 1924 8th St NW Washington, DC 20001 Lease Terms: Variable All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EC88F77C568344",
