        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post The Shay 1924 8th St NW Washington, DC 20001 A wonderful home in Washington is waiting for you! Reach out via phone: show contact info We currently have a gorgeous Studio bedroom 1 bathroom with Call. Monthly Price: $1804 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Welcome to The Shay, a luxury apartment community designed for modern, vibrant living in Shaw- Washington, D.C's most exciting neighborhood. From inspired shopping and bustling nightlife to top-notch restaurants and live music, these sleek and stylish apartment homes let you live where you play. With the excitement of 9th and U streets just a short walk away, The Shay can help you create your own definition of home. Community Highlights: ➢ 24 Hour Availability ➢ Breakfast/Coffee Concierge ➢ Community-Wide WiFi ➢ Controlled Access for Residents Only ➢ Covered Parking ➢ High Speed WiFi in Common Areas ➢ Online Services ➢ On-Site Management Dedicated to Service Excellence ➢ Package Receiving ➢ Smoke-Free ➢ 24-hour Fitness Center with Free Weights ➢ Beautiful Lobby and High Speed Elevators ➢ Fire Pit and Seating Area ➢ Game Area with Billiards, Foosball, and More ➢ Incredible Access to Shopping, Cafes, Dining, and Retail right downstairs ➢ Monumental Views ➢ One Block from Shaw Metro Station - Yellow/Green Line ➢ On-Site Retail ➢ Reflecting Pool ➢ Sparkling Pool with Lounge Chairs and Umbrellas Apartment Home Highlights: ➢ Built in Pantry Cabinet ➢ Central Heat and Air Conditioning ➢ Ideal Work from Home Layouts ➢ Oversized Stainless Steel Smart Appliances ➢ Slip Grip Tubs ➢ Spacious 10 foot ceilings ➢ Studio, Loft, One- to 2 Bedroom Plus Den Floorplans ➢ Terraced Patio/Balconies with select floorplans ➢ Beautiful Hardwood Flooring Throughout ➢ Custom Kitchen Cabinetry with Quartz Countertops ➢ Floor to Ceiling Windows ➢ Full-Sized, Stacked, In-unit Washer and Dryer ➢ Incredible DC Skyline Views ➢ Moveable Kitchen Islands in Select Apartment Homes ➢ Porcelain Matte Finished Bathroom Tile ➢ Rain Shower Heads Reach out via phone: show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/theshaydc Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=shay&rp=dCyremLEKK2y&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=shay&rp=dCyremLEKK2y&t=sch Leasing Options: Variable Pet Policy: We understand pets are a huge part of good living. The Shay welcomes both cats and dogs in our apartment homes. Note we do have some restrictions please view our full pet policy below. Max 2 Allowed. One-time Fee: $500. Rent: $60 Per Pet. Restrictions: Breed Restrictions All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY IKC2N0TK5B7GNIN",
