ney Road, left or right onto Robey Terrace Maximum Income Limits may apply: 50% 1 person - $57,400 or 60% 1 person - $68,880 50% 2 people - $65,600 or 60% 2 person - $78,720 50% 3 people - $73,800 or 60% 3 person - $88,560 50% 4 people - $81,950 or 60% 4 person - $98,340 50% 5 people - $88,550 or 60% 5 person - $106,260 50% 6 people - $95,100 or 60% 6 person - $114,120 50% 7 people - $101,650 or 60% 7 person - $121,980 50% 8 people - $108,200 or 60% 8 person - $129,840 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 671AC1C3C1B347A",
