        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Crescent Park Village Leasing Office: 2 Elmira St SE Washington, DC 20032 Contact us for more information! show contact info Take a look at what Crescent Park Village has to offer! You'll appreciate the neighborhood amenities near Crescent Park Village. This part of Washington is relatively bike friendly so you can ride to most local destinations. Neighborhood parks offer a welcome respite. Like walking around town? You'll find streets lined with sidewalks that are well-lit at night. While many residents at Crescent Park Village do own a car, Washington public transportation is nearby. There is ample space for residents' vehicles in the uncovered parking lots. Street parking is also plentiful if you have guests. Rental Information: 1 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom / 710 sq ft Monthly Price: $1390 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Amenities: Additional Information: ✓ Bike friendly ✓ Highways Nearby ✓ Laundry Facilities ✓ Near Downtown ✓ On-site parking ✓ Parks Nearby ✓ Playground ✓ Well lit streets ✓ Availability 24 Hours ✓ Controlled Access/Gated ✓ Easy street parking ✓ Heavy Car Traffic Area ✓ Older/Historical Building ✓ On-Site Management & Maintenance ✓ Pay Your Rent Online ✓ Public Transportation Nearby ✓ Sidewalk Lined Streets ✓ Tree Lined Streets Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Contact us for more information! show contact info Pet Policy: Call for information Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=crescent_park_village&rp=7q6Wm85fwAk4&t=wb Floor plan measurements are approximate and are for illustrative purposes only. While we do not doubt the floor plan's accuracy, we make no guarantee, warranty or representation as to the accuracy and completeness of the floor plan. You and or your advisers should conduct a careful, independent investigation of the property to determine to your satisfaction as to the suitability of the property for your space requirements. Income restrictions apply. Please call for more details. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A85472E89C72459",
