        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Key Towers 6060 Tower Ct Alexandria, VA 22304 Contact: show contact info . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 1 BR - 1 BA - 875 sq ft Monthly Price: $1806 - $2035 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Conveniently located, our apartments provide easy access to major routes including I-95, I-395, I-495, Route 236, Route 7, and Route 50. When you're ready to explore, enjoy fantastic shopping and dining at National Harbor, Pentagon City Mall, and the lively Kingstow, Springfield, and Potomac Yard shopping centers. Nature enthusiasts will appreciate nearby outdoor adventures at Loftridge, Belle Haven, Lake Barcroft, and Lake Accotink Parks. Your perfect Alexandria living experience begins here! . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: ● Elevator ● Fitness Center ● Free Weights ● Off Street Parking ● Penthouse ● Pool ● Recycling ● Smart Package 365 ● Sundeck ● *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ● Controlled Access/Gated ● Flexible Rent Payment Options with FLEX ● Laundry Facilities Onsite ● On-Site Maintenance ● On-Site Management ● Public Transportation ● Report Rent and Build Credit with IDIQ ● WIFI in Common Areas . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment 