        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom | 1115 - 1120 sq ft Monthly Price: $2087 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Paxton 1611 Benning Rd NE Washington, DC 20002 Contact Info: show contact info Description: INCOME RESTRICTIONS APPLY Near the H Street corridor and close to Metro, Paxton Apartments is an affordable apartment home community with the highest-quality design and community focus built into its very foundation. With a welcome combination of beautiful residences, smart gathering spaces and resident services from a professional management team, you can have the best of all that an engaged community and a peaceful home can offer. Paxton is your place to live well. Apartment Amenities: ❖ Above Counter Microwave ❖ Ample Closet and Storage Space ❖ Complete Stainless Steel Appliance Package ❖ In Home Washer and Dryer ❖ Natural Light from Large Windows ❖ Plank Flooring ❖ Sleek Kitchens with Shaker Style Cabinets and Quartz Countertops Our Residents Enjoy: ❖ Bicycle Storage ❖ Clubhouse ❖ Fitness Center with cardio equipment, weights and room to stretch ❖ Fob access provides an added layer of ease and comfort ❖ Package Lockers and Package Room ❖ Professional management will be on hand to ensure that all residents feel welcome and at home ❖ The Paxton Club- lounge area with games, TV and direct access to the courtyard ❖ New Construction Additional Details: Deposit: Call Terms: 12-Month Pets: No Pets Allowed. Contact Info: show contact info Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=paxton&rp=agxNoqWCeyH6&t=wb All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 13CD0SZO1B41KR",
