        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post -- The Villas at Langley -- Phone: show contact info Special-Especial Move in by 6/19/26 & receive 1 month free + waived prorated rent on select homes. Exclusions may apply. Contact the leasing office for details. Mundate antes del 6/19/26 y recibe hasta 1 mes gratuito en viviendas seleccionadas. Pueden aplicarse exclusiones. Ponte en contacto con la oficina de arrendamiento para obtener mas detalles. Monthly Price: $1799 - $2033 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment: 2 Bedroom | 1 Bathroom Square Footage: 992 sq ft Our community offers appealing apartments and a location that makes it easy to commute using either public transportation or your own car. Villas at Langley is the place to live. Situated along I-495 minutes from DC and steps from Metro's Silver and Blue lines, Haven Largo is a restorative retreat with direct access to commuter hubs, University of Maryland Capital Region Medical Center, and extensive shopping and dining options at Carillon and Woodmore Towne Centre. Surrounded by breathtaking parks, Haven Largo offers fresh air and fresh entertainment in equal measure. Pet Policy: Max 2 Allowed | One time Fee $250 | Rent $25 Restrictions: Breed Restrictions Apply Check out our beautiful community featuring: ❖ 24 Hour Access ❖ 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance ❖ Basketball Court ❖ Enclosed Soccer Field ❖ Large Swimming Pool ❖ Laundry Centers in Each Building ❖ Online Services ❖ Outdoor BBQ Grills ❖ Playground ❖ Property Manager on Site ❖ 1 Mile from the Adelphi Recreation Center ❖ CASA de Maryland On-Site ❖ Close to Langley Park - McCormick Elementary School ❖ Easy Access to MD Rt 2, MD 313 and MD 235 ❖ Easy Access to Public Transportation ❖ Hospitals Nearby: Washington Adventist Hospital and Holy Cross Hospital ❖ Park-Like Community with Outdoor Seating ❖ Shopping Nearby: Langely Park Plaza, Prince George's Plaza and K-Mart Apartment features include: ❖ Ample Parking ❖ Dining Room ❖ Double-Pane Windows ❖ Garbage Disposal ❖ Gas Heat ❖ Large, Eat-In Kitchen in select units ❖ Patio or Balcony Available ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Spacious Closets ❖ Tub/Shower Phone: show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Wed: 11:00 AM - 5:30 PM Thu - Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=a4H4cx4L8q7D&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=a4H4cx4L8q7D&t=ap 8100 15th Ave Hyattsville, MD 20783 Lease Terms: 12-Month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY E735A3CCA5EA41",
