tures include: ❖ Ample Parking ❖ Dining Room ❖ Double-Pane Windows ❖ Garbage Disposal ❖ Gas Heat ❖ Large, Eat-In Kitchen in select units ❖ Patio or Balcony Available ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Spacious Closets ❖ Tub/Shower Phone: show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Wed: 11:00 AM - 5:30 PM Thu - Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=a4H4cx4L8q7D&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=villas_at_langley&rp=a4H4cx4L8q7D&t=ap 8100 15th Ave Hyattsville, MD 20783 Lease Terms: 12-Month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY E735A3CCA5EA41",
