        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Quebec Arms Apartments Leasing Office: 1400 Merrimac Dr Hyattsville, MD 20783 Phone Number: show contact info Take a look at what Quebec Arms Apartments has to offer! When you're ready to venture out, the best of Hyattsville is just outside your doorstep including exciting restaurants, entertainment, shops and more. If you're in the mood for outdoor fun Hyattsville offers great parks and activities including Langley Park Community Center and Langley Hampshire Neighborhood Park and more! Of course, you'll also enjoy quality schools in the Prince Georges County school district. At Quebec Arms, the options are endless. Let us show you your new home. Call today to schedule a tour. If you are looking for more room to grow without sacrificing location, this expansive two-bedroom residence at Quebec Arms is exactly what you need. Our floor plans are among the largest in the neighborhood, featuring a chef-friendly kitchen with ample cabinet space and two king-sized bedrooms that offer the privacy and comfort you deserve. Now Offering One Month Free! This is the ideal spot for anyone who wants to be in the heart of the action, located just minutes from the West Hyattsville Metro and the premier shopping and dining at the Mall at Prince Georges. You will be steps away from groceries, entertainment, and the scenic trails of the Northwest Branch Park. We offer a community-focused atmosphere with 24-hour emergency maintenance and off-street parking for your convenience. Hablamos Espanol. Our team is ready to help you find your perfect fit, and because we speak Spanish, we can ensure a smooth and welcoming leasing experience for everyone. Schedule your private tour today to experience this incredible space in person. Income restrictions apply. Qualification is based on household size and verified income. Please contact the leasing office for details One Month Free Rental Information: 2 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom / 883 sq ft Monthly Price: $1850 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Amenities: ● Beautiful hardwood floors, some carpeted apartment homes ● Garbage Disposal ● Generous room sizes ● High Speed Internet Access ● Individually controlled heating and air conditioning ● Mini blinds in all windows ● One, two, and three bedroom apartment homes ● Spacious Closets Additional Information: ● 1 block to Metro ● Controlled Access ● On-site management ● Playground ● Some Paid Utilities ● Central laundry facility ● Close to Downtown Silver Spring and DC ● On-site Maintenance ● Shuttlebus service to University of MD ● Walking distance to shopping center Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Sat: 9:00 AM - 3:00 PM Phone Number: show contact info Pet Policy: No pets allowed; Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=2ZNVZVwREcnS&t=wb 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=2ZNVZVwREcnS&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quebec_arms&rp=2ZNVZVwREcnS&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 6ACCB50580EF4FBC",
