        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1855 - $2965 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Haven Huntley Meadows: 7300 Jon Paul Dr Alexandria, VA 22306 Apartment for Rent: 2-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 815 sq ft | Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month Call us: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ❖ 24-hour maintenance ❖ Children's playground ❖ Dedicated on-site management team ❖ Flexible Rent Payment Options with FLEX ❖ Off-street parking ❖ Outdoor sport court ❖ Proximate to Huntley Meadows Park ❖ Report Rent and Build Credit with IDIQ ❖ Smoke Free ❖ *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program.* ❖ Accessibility to major bus stops as well as biking and walking trails ❖ Convenient clubhouse and resident lounge ❖ Minutes from I-495, Old Town Alexandria, and Mount Vernon ❖ Pre-installed Cox Wi-Fi with one month free ❖ Sun-drenched courtyard and grilling patio with social seating ❖ Within a mile of Giant, Shoppers, and extensive restaurants and retailers APARTMENT AMENITIES ❖ Central air conditioning and heat ❖ Custom countertops ❖ Gas ranges ❖ High Speed Internet Access ❖ Plush carpeting ❖ Private balconies and terraces ❖ Contemporary kitchens with dishwashers in Select Units ❖ Energy-efficient appliances in black or white ❖ Large windows offering ample natural light ❖ Light and dark wood cabinetry options ❖ Modern vinyl plank flooring in select units ❖ Spacious walk-in closets ❖ Versatile one-, two-, and three-bedroom floor plans with townhome options ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Choose comfort at Haven Huntley Meadows, inviting Alexandria apartments designed to help you thrive. Set the right tone in spacious one-, two-, and three-bedroom residences filled with natural light, and savor scenic strolls through lushly landscaped grounds. Embrace ease from the convenience of family-friendly amenities and nearby bus access to the perks of dependable on-site management and a relaxing outdoor scene. Haven is your personal oasis. Pet Policy: Haven Huntley Meadows is a paw-friendly community. Cats and dogs up to 50 pounds are permitted with the payment of a one-time, $300 fee and an additional $35 per month in rent. Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=haven_huntley_meadows&rp=xtqzrcN3CBfi&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=haven_huntley_meadows&rp=xtqzrcN3CBfi&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=haven_huntley_meadows&rp=xtqzrcN3CBfi&t=trt Call us: show contact info All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 598558CBC1BA403F",
