        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to Potomac Woods Senior Living! Located at: 2001 Southhampton St Woodbridge, VA 22191 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 1 # of Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 566 - 604 sq ft Monthly Price: $1341 - $1371 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call for details: show contact info Senior living with respect! Sited on four beautifully wooded acres in Woodbridge, VA, Potomac Woods Senior Living Community offers convenience, comfort, and community for independent seniors. Designed for affordable, independent senior living, this three-story, controlled access elevator building features one and two-bedroom pet-friendly apartment living. Each apartment home is fully equipped with wall-to-wall carpeting, all electric kitchens with dishwashers, individually controlled heating and air conditioning, washer and dryer hookups, and available balconies. A large Resident Lounge on the lobby level has a kitchen for resident functions or large group entertaining. Residents also have complimentary access to a craft and game room, library, and exercise facility. The beautifully landscaped outdoor spaces, patio and resident gardens are ideal for enjoying nature. Community Features: ➢ Disability Access ➢ Elevator ➢ Fitness Center ➢ Guest Parking ➢ On-Line Payments ➢ Onsite Maintenance ➢ Pet Friendly ➢ Shopping Nearby ➢ Smoke-Free ➢ Verizon FiOS ➢ Community Laundry Room ➢ Community Room with Kitchen ➢ Community/Onsite Parking ➢ Emergency Maintenance ➢ Game Room with Billiards Table ➢ Income Restrictions Apply ➢ Outdoor Dining Area ➢ Public Transportation ➢ Recycling Available ➢ Section 8 Vouchers Accepted Apartment Home Features: ➢ Disability Access ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Dual Pane Windows ➢ Elevator(s) ➢ Garbage Disposal ➢ Handicap Access Units ➢ Mini Blinds ➢ View ➢ Washer & Dryer Connections ➢ Washer Dryer Hookup ➢ Contemporary finishes ➢ Emergency pull cords, sprinklers, smoke detectors ➢ Fully-equipped all elecric kitchens Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call for details: show contact info Pet Policy: Allowed: Small pets (under 25 lbs). Deposit: $200. Monthly Pet Rent: $25. Leasing Options: 12-Month Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=potomac_woods_senior_living&rp=4xTcbuE9UzHU&t=wb All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 08C65300D63C41B",
