        "geocode_query": "2315 Blueridge Ave #14",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Amherst Square 2315 Blueridge Ave #14 Wheaton, MD 20902 Contact Info: show contact info . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 1 - 4 BR - 1 - 1.5 BA - 820 - 1300 sq ft Monthly Price: $1591 - $2500 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 12-Month . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" Amherst Square is in a prime location boasting many conveniences and amenities. Convenient to the metro, shopping and minutes to DC, Amherst Square combines value and convenience together for easy living. These apartments offer dishwashers, classic hardwood floors, air-conditioning, and cable ready/Internet access. Community amenities include laundry rooms in each building, playgrounds, and a community center that offers summer programs for the residents. Come and visit Amherst Square today! . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: ❖ Community Center ❖ Easy access to I-495,I-270,I-95 ❖ Easy Access to Major Roadways ❖ Laundry Facility ❖ Playground ❖ Convenient to MARC commuter train ❖ Convenient to nearby Silver Spring, Takoma Park, and Washington D.C. ❖ Near Retail, Restaurants and Entertainment ❖ Walk to Wheaton Metro (Red Line) . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment Home Comes With: ❖ Cable Ready ❖ Central Air Conditioning ❖ Classic Refinished Wood Flooring ❖ Formal Dining Room ❖ Full Kitchen with Window ❖ Garbage Disposal ❖ High Speed Internet Available ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Storage and Closet Space . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Contact Info: -- show contact info -- Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=amherst_square&rp=2vtJuFsFwEft&t=wb Pets: $25 monthly pet rent. $350 deposit per pet nonrefundable. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Income Restrictions for Amherst Square # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $49,260       2 People   -   $56,280       3 People   -   $63,300       4 People   -   $70,320       5 People   -   $75,960       6 People   -   $81,600 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. Income Limits Apply - Please ask a Leasing Consultant for details. Minimum Income Requirements: 1 Bedroom - $40,920 2 Bedroom - $48,930 3 Bedroom - $56,310 4 Bedroom - $56,880 Application fee - $15 per adult member over the age of 18. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EA6A83B43D9647D1",
