th Window ❖ Garbage Disposal ❖ High Speed Internet Available ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Storage and Closet Space . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Contact Info: -- show contact info -- Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=amherst_square&rp=2vtJuFsFwEft&t=wb Pets: $25 monthly pet rent. $350 deposit per pet nonrefundable. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Income Restrictions for Amherst Square # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $49,260       2 People   -   $56,280       3 People   -   $63,300       4 People   -   $70,320       5 People   -   $75,960       6 People   -   $81,600 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. Income Limits Apply - Please ask a Leasing Consultant for details. Minimum Income Requirements: 1 Bedroom - $40,920 2 Bedroom - $48,930 3 Bedroom - $56,310 4 Bedroom - $56,880 Application fee - $15 per adult member over the age of 18. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EA6A83B43D9647D1",
