        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Takoma Towers Bedroom: 3 | Bathroom: 1 Square Footage: 928 sq ft Monthly Price: $1935 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Community Description Takoma Towers is your best home on the border of Washington, D.C. and Prince George's County, Maryland. With a Washington Metro bus stop right outside the apartments (Routes k6 & k9), and just minutes from the Purple Line, Takoma Towers is an easy commute to work in DC and surrounding areas. We're near shopping, groceries, restaurants and entertainment. We're a short drive from hiking through Rock Creek Park, University of Maryland Observatory, and lots, lots more. Enjoy the convenience of city life in the suburban comfort of Maryland. 3 Bedroom 1 Bath - 928 Sqft 3 bd, 1 ba | Available Now Discover comfortable and convenient living at Takoma Towers, a premier apartment community nestled in the vibrant neighborhood of Takoma Park, Maryland-just minutes from Washington, D.C. Ideal for professionals, families, and commuters alike, Takoma Towers offers thoughtfully designed apartments with modern features and a wide range of on-site amenities to enhance your lifestyle. Community Amenities Include: • 24-hour laundry facilities for your convenience • On-site Amazon Locker for secure and easy package delivery • Controlled access entry for added security and peace of mind • Fully equipped fitness center to support your active lifestyle • Refreshing swimming pool perfect for relaxing and staying cool • Landscaped courtyard ideal for unwinding outdoors • Spacious clubhouse for social events and gatherings • Safe and fun playground for children and families • Available storage units to meet your extra space needs • Elevator access to all floors for added comfort and mobility Located just a short ride from downtown D.C., Takoma Towers combines the charm of suburban living with easy access to the cultural, professional, and entertainment opportunities of the nation's capital. Schedule a tour today and experience the exceptional lifestyle at Takoma Towers. Online application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=takoma_towers&rp=us2JCsap7gLM&t=ap Amenities Black Appliances Grey Floor Porch Granite Countertops Upgraded Kitchen Cabinets Rental Terms Rent: $1,935 Application Fee: $25 Available Now Pet Policy Cats not allowed Dogs not allowed Appliances Fridge Stove Community Amenities ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Elevators ➢ Grill Station ➢ Onsite Laundry Facility ➢ Outdoor Playground ➢ Patios & Balconies ➢ Preferred Parking ➢ Spacious Floor Plans ➢ Walk-In Closet ➢ Breathtaking Views ➢ Community Room ➢ Sparkling Swimming Pool ➢ State-of-the-art Fitness Center ➢ Yoga Room Apartment Features Contact Information Visit Us: 6731 New Hampshire Ave #0010 Takoma Park, MD 20912 Call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=takoma_towers&rp=us2JCsap7gLM&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=takoma_towers&rp=us2JCsap7gLM&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=takoma_towers&rp=us2JCsap7gLM&t=sch Additional Details Pet Policy: No Pets Allowed Lease Terms: 12-Month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 303ILJLCIDDO3M",
