        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Apply to receive one month free* Offer only eligible up to 48-hours after touring! Towns at Andrew's Park 5925 Allentown Andres Dr. , Suitland, MD, 20746 Follow This Link for More Information: https://avenue5.aptfeatures.com/xfwmrm Call Now - show contact info x 220 OR Text 220 to show contact info to contact our leasing team. Move to a Stunning Camp Springs Rental Community 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath | Approximately 2400 Sq. Ft. Community Info: Newly designed in an incredible location, your new Camp Springs rental home near Andrews Airforce Base lets residents experience a true hidden gem. Enjoy a warm, neighborhood feel in an ideal location right off I-495. Our three and four-bedroom townhomes are thoughtfully appointed with elevated finishes and amenities designed to provide comfort and a sense of home.   Unit Highlights ✧  Open Concept Living ✧  High End Finishes ✧  New Townhomes ✧  Double Vanities ✧  Expansive 2400 sqf ✧  A Must See ✧  Walk-In Closets ✧  Powder Room ✧  Private Balconies ✧  Private Two-Car Garage ✧  Eat-In Kitchen ✧  Top Line Stainless Appliances ✧  Washer and Dryer In-Unit ✧  Beautiful Wood Flooring ✧  Granite Countertops ✧  Large Kitchen Islands Community Highlights ✧  Bus Stop Located Directly Outside Community ✧  Short Distance to Branch Avenue Metro Station ✧  Prime Location Right off I-495 ✧  Tour Today ✧  One Mile from Joint Base Andrews ✧  Playground ✧  Onsite Retail: Dominos, Advanced Auto Parts, & Wawa Office Hours Tuesday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Pet Policy Pets Allowed Finding a pet friendly apartment can be difficult at times. We know how much you love your furry friends, and we are pleased to welcome four-legged residents to Towns at Andrews Park. We love your pets as much as you do. Please speak with an associate for more details. Equal Housing Opportunity CWeXgv7E",
