        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 765 Sq. Ft. Want more info on this unit? See the link (below): https://glick.aptdetails.com/p0m6me Call Now - show contact info x 94 OR Text 94 to show contact info for more information. Discover your new beginning! Community Info: The Woods of Fairfax Apartments in Lorton, VA is a relaxed community just 15 minutes from the Metro station and 30 minutes from Washington D.C that provides apartment homes in Fairfax, County, VA. This newly renovated community offers one, two, and three bedroom apartment homes with quartz counter tops and plank flooring. Residents enjoy amenities such as a fitness center, bark park, swimming pools with sun decks, grill stations, play parks, and more. Features: ‣  Abundance of Closet Space ‣  Completely Renovated Units ‣  Full Tub with Ceramic Tile Surround ‣  Upgrades Everywhere ‣  Washer & Dryer ‣  Fully-equipped Kitchen-Including Dishwasher ‣  Scenic Wooded Views [ 1 ] ‣  Stylish Finishes ‣  New Stainless Appliances ‣  1, 2, & 3 Bedroom Apartment Homes ‣  New Wood Style Flooring ‣  Cozy, Wood-burning Fireplaces [ 1 ] ‣  A Must See 1. Select Units Community Amenities: ‣  Resident Referral Bonus ‣  Car Wash Station ‣  Lighted Sports & Tennis Courts ‣  Planned Community Events ‣  Online Rent Payments & Maintenance Requests ‣  Active Duty Military & Federal Employee Discounts ‣  Pool ‣  Flexible Leases 2 - 15 months ‣  Professional Management & Maintenance Team ‣  Fitness on Demand ‣  Tour Today ‣  Grill Stations with Picnic Tables ‣  Fun Play Parks ‣  Covered Parking ‣  Parcel Lockers Pet Policy: The Woods of Fairfax is a pet-friendly community - Fees and Restrictions apply - Call for details. Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Woods of Fairfax 7630 Fairfield Woods Court, Lorton, VA, 22079 Equal Housing Opportunity Dl9hlH24Eb",
