        "geocode_query": "16573 Nanticoke Way near Powells Creek",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 2 Baths: 2 Square Feet: 836 Interested in more information? Visit link below: https://Fairfield-apts.com/i3l4rv Three Great Options For Affordable Living In Woodbridge, VA Call Now - show contact info x 67 OR Text 67 to show contact info to contact us.   Community Info Riverwoods Apartments, Riverwoods at Towne Square & Riverwoods at Lake Ridge are pleased to offer affordable living in our 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartments and townhomes. Live the lifestyle you deserve at the price you can afford. Income limits apply. Residence Features ✩  Pet Friendly - Puppies And Kittens Welcome (Breed Restrictions Apply) ✩  Oversized Closet ✩  Fully Equipped Kitchen Including A Disposal And Dishwasher ✩  Ceiling Fan ✩  Tons Of Natural Light ✩  In-Home Washer And Dryer ✩  Kitchen Island With Breakfast Bar ✩  Breakfast Bar ✩  Wood-Look Flooring In Kitchen And Bathroom ✩  Kitchen Pantry ✩  Air Conditioning Community Features ✩  Playground ✩  Pool With Spacious Sun Deck ✩  Proximity To Potomac Mills Mall, Medical Services, Quantico Base, And Fort Belvoir ✩  Children's Wading Pool ✩  On-Site Maintenance ✩  Ample Parking ✩  Minutes To The River Oaks Shopping Center ✩  Picnic And BBQ Area ✩  Garage Parking At Select Communities ✩  Public Transportation ✩  Clubhouse ✩  On-Site Management ✩  Proximity To I-95 And Rte. 1 ✩  Fitness Center Pet Policy Dogs and cats, including puppies and kittens under 1 year old, are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check and shots by 6 months of age. A signed animal addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. $500 deposit per pet $50/month per pets Income Requirements Current Income Limits 1 person: $63,300 2 people: $72,360 3 people: $81,420 4 people: $90,420 5 people: $97,680 6 people: $104,940 7 people: $112,140 Office Hours Monday-Tuesday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Wednesday: 11:00AM-5:00PM Thursday-Friday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Photos on this ad may not reflect all floorplans. Advertised pricing and availability are subject to change without notice and cannot be guaranteed. Equal Housing Opportunity sX3eDej0nJTI",
