        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 1 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 1057 Interested in more information? See link below: https://lerner.aptsup.com/abjvc8 Live better then ever at our beautifully wooded community in Greenbelt, Maryland. Call Now - show contact info x 131 OR Text 131 to show contact info for more information.   Community Info Surrounded by acres of green space with mature landscaping and tall shade trees, Lerner University Square is a hidden gem in Greenbelt, Maryland. As a resident, you will have exclusive access to community amenities, such as a sparkling swimming pool, basketball court, and playground. Inside the apartments, you'll enjoy fully equipped kitchens, completely renovated with granite countertops and maple cabinets, and all apartments include a washer and dryer. With nearby access to the Greenbelt Metro/MARC and New Carrollton Metro/Amtrak Station and easy access to I-95 and the Capital Beltway, getting around town has never been so easy. If that weren't enough, we also have metro bus stops and a University of Maryland shuttle stop located within the community to take you to University of Maryland and other nearby shopping and dining destinations. Lerner University Square is the only community you should consider calling \"home\". Residence Features ✩  Eat-In Kitchens in Most Apartments ✩  Spacious Floor Plans ✩  Renovated Apartment Homes ✩  In-Home Washers and Dryers ✩  Equipped Kitchens ✩  Oversized, Private Balconies and Patios ✩  Pantry Cabinets ✩  Modern Appliances ✩  Walk-In Closets in All Apartments Community Features ✩  Plentiful, Free Parking ✩  Resident-Exclusive Events ✩  Playground ✩  Convenient Location ✩  Sparkling Swimming Pool ✩  24/7 Maintenance ✩  Controlled Access Buildings ✩  Basketball Court ✩  Fitness Center ✩  Nearby Entertainment ✩  Pet-Friendly Pet Policy Fee: $350 Rent: $50 Office Hours Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity V9CWTKyqU7",
