        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 1069 Sq. Ft. Interested In This Unit? Use this link for more details: https://lerner.aptsup.com/jnugi6 Call Now - show contact info x 325 OR Text 325 to show contact info to text us. Apartment Living That Fits Your Life Community Info: At Lerner Surrey Square, you will experience peaceful, garden-style living on Pennsylvania Avenue just minutes from Washington, D.C. If you're looking for recreational options, this lovely community includes a sparkling swimming pool, barbeque and picnic areas, two playgrounds, and it's adjacent to Park Berkshire. The spacious apartments include a private balcony or patio, wall-to-wall carpet, abundant closet space, fully equipped kitchens with modern appliances, and some were recently renovated with granite countertops and oak cabinets. You will appreciate the effortless access to the Capital Beltway, Route 4, and direct routing to the nearby Suitland Metro Station. Not only is Lerner Surrey Square situated near Samuel P. Massie, a top-rated elementary school, it is also in an ideal location for employees of Andrews Air Force Base, UPS, Verizon, Maryland Hospital Center, and the U.S. Census Bureau. Comfortable apartments, a great location, and unbeatable customer service are what will make you want to call Lerner Surrey Square home. Features: ‣  Abundant Closet Space ‣  Furnished Apartments Available ‣  Renovated Kitchens* ‣  Spacious Floor Plans ‣  Oak Cabinets* ‣  Eat-In Kitchens ‣  Granite Countertops* ‣  Wall-To-Wall Carpet ‣  Oversized, Private Balconies and Patios ‣  Modern Appliances ‣  Equipped Kitchens Community Amenities: ‣  Easy Access to Prince George's Community College and Forestville Military Academy ‣  Near Reagan Washington National Airport and Andrews Air Force Base ‣  Gated Community ‣  Plentiful, Free Parking ‣  Resident-Exclusive Events ‣  BBQ and Picnic Area ‣  Two Playgrounds ‣  Close to the Suitland Metro with Metro Bus Stop at Community ‣  Great Location ‣  Easy Access to Washington, D.C.'s Greatest Landmarks and Nightlife ‣  Now Showing ‣  Minutes to Suitland Community Center ‣  A Must See ‣  Olympic-Sized Swimming Pool ‣  24/7 Maintenance ‣  Pet-Friendly ‣  Close to Shopping and Dining at Forest Village Park Mall ‣  Located on Pennsylvania Avenue Just Inside the Capital Beltway (I-495) Pet Policy: Allowed | One time Fee $200 Rent $30 Restrictions: Lerner Surrey Square is a pet-friendly apartment community in Forestville, Maryland. A maximum of up to 2 pets per home are permitted and pet rent is applicable to each pet. The $200 pet fee per pet is non-refundable. Breed restrictions apply and no exotic pets. Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Surrey Square 6024 Surrey Square, Forestville, MD, 20747 Equal Housing Opportunity y5ii6cMYo1",
