        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This 4 bedroom, 2 bath brick home sits on a third acre lot in Groveton Heights. Hardwood floors, wood burning fireplace, and a bonus room off the kitchen that leads to the patio. Kitchen has stainless appliances and good cabinet space. Basement has a bedroom, full bath and its own walkup entrance. Backyard is fully fenced with mature trees and a gated driveway. Detached 2 car garage with storage above. Water heater and roof both done in 2022. Close to Bucknell Elementary, Sandburg Middle and West Potomac High School. Walmart, Costco and Wegmans nearby on Richmond Hwy. Huntley Meadows Park is just down the road. Easy access to Rt 1, 495 and Huntington Metro. No smoking. Small pets ok. Showings Tuesday and Wednesday 1:30-2:30, Friday 4:30-5:30, Sat/Sun 9-10am. If interested, send your name, number and when you're looking to move in.",
