        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  2 Square Feet:  1081 Date Available:  2026-07-21 Address:  4201 Jefferson Oaks Cir Our community is proud to highlight its Walk Score (Very Walkable) and Bike Score (Very Bikeable)! Welcome home to The Jefferson at Fair Oaks! Our fabulous community is located in Fairfax, Virginia. Here you will find a beautiful established community with the convenience of being in the heart of everything. With easy access to numerous highways, including Interstate 66, your stressful commute will be a thing of the past. Shopping, dining, and entertainment are all within walking distance of your front door. If being outdoors is more your style, there are several public parks and historical sites close by. Amenities Include: Carpeted Floors Scenic Trails 24-Hour State-of-the-art Fitness Center Central Air and Heating All-electric Kitchen Shimmering Swimming Pool Breakfast Bar Cable Ready Clubhouse with WiFi Ceiling Fans Beautiful Landscaping Pet Friendly Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://liveklingbeil.com/cqxothk7/jefferson-at-fair-oaks *Pricing and availability subject to change at any time; rent ranges reflected are estimates. Any specials, offers or promotions displayed are valid for new applicants only; terms and conditions apply. Any specials, offers, promotions or events are subject to change or expiration at any time; information is not guaranteed to be accurate or timely due to syndication delays or other technical/programming reasons. Please contact leasing office for the most up-to-date information. Credit/background screening and application approval is required. Renderings are an artist's conception and are intended only as a general reference. Features, materials, finishes and layout of subject unit may be different than shown in images.",
