        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Great Hope Homes Monthly Price: $2700 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 1709 sq ft BEDROOMS: 5 BATHROOMS: 2 LEASE TERMS: 12-Month Call us today at show contact info APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: ✓ Cabinet Space ✓ Carpet ✓ Gas Stove ✓ High-Speed Internet Access ✓ Linen Closet ✓ Parking Space ✓ Refrigerator ✓ Window Coverings ✓ Air Conditioning ✓ Large eat-in kitchen ✓ Tile Flooring in kitchen and bathroom ✓ Window Coverings Don't miss your opportunity to lease a beautiful townhome at an AMAZING price! Great Hope Homes Townhome community is nestled in a beautiful wooded lot (off Good Hope Drive near New Hampshire Avenue). Silver Spring offers an attractive balance between suburban and city lifestyles. With plenty of residential areas throughout, it provides a tranquil suburban retreat from the noise and chaos of a city. At the same time, downtown Silver Spring has some of the best music venues, restaurants and shopping in all of Maryland. PROPERTY FEATURES: ✓ Basketball Court ✓ Business Center ✓ Clubhouse ✓ Community Playground ✓ Community/Onsite Parking ✓ Multi Use Room ✓ On-Premise Laundry ✓ Public Transportation Accessibility- Metro Bus Lines Z2 & 39 ✓ Walking Paths ✓ An Abundance of FREE Surface Parking ✓ Charles Drew Elementary School ✓ Community Center with Meeting/Social Room and Computer lab ✓ Francis Scott Key Middle School ✓ Near Maydale Nature Center ✓ New Hampshire Ave and Good Hope Road ✓ Quiet Silver Spring Neighborhood ✓ Springbrook Blake High School PET POLICY: Pet friendly community. Breed Restriction Weight Restriction - No Aggressive Breeds. $25 Monthly Pet Rent. $300 Pet Deposit. 45 lbs. Weight Limit.  Please speak with a member of the leasing team for further details. VISIT US TODAY! 1081 Good Hope Dr Silver Spring, MD 20905 Call us today at show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=great_hope&rp=8VK2mi3E7NaK&t=wb Maximum Income Limits: 50% 1 person - $57,400 or 60%1 person - $68,880 50% 2 people - $65,600 or 60% 2 person - $78,720 50% 3 people - $73,800 or 60% 3 person - $88,560 50% 4 people - $81,950 or 60% 4 person - $98,340 50% 5 people - $88,550 or 60% 5 person - $106,260 50% 6 people - $95,100 or 60% 6 person - $114,120 50% 7 people - $101,650 or 60% 7 person - $121,980 50% 8 people - $108,200 or 60% 8 person - $129,840 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY DAC4E44154A24AF6",
