        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Hyattsville House Apartments 6000 42nd Ave Hyattsville, MD 20781 Contact Info: show contact info Apartment Information: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bath Apartment Size: 807 sq ft Monthly Price: $1530 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Includes: ❖ Balconies and Patios ❖ Cable Ready ❖ Ceiling Fans ❖ Central Air Conditioning and Heat, thermostats in every room ❖ Disposal ❖ Gas Range ❖ Handrails ❖ High Speed Internet Access ❖ Large Windows ❖ Oven ❖ Pest Control ❖ Range ❖ Refrigerator/Freezer ❖ Smoke Free ❖ Spacious Floorplans ❖ Storage Space ❖ Wall-to-Wall Carpeting ❖ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ❖ Yard Property Description: Hyattsville House offers easy access to Washington and Baltimore via the West Hyattsville and Prince George's Plaza stops on the Metro system's Green Line or by MARC commuter rail trains on the Camden Line in the neighboring town of Riverdale Park. We are across the street from Hyattsville Middle School and within walking distance of Hyattsville Elementary School, St. Jerome Academy, and DeMatha Catholic High School; the bus stop for Northwestern High School is across the street. The Historic District of Hyattsville is home to several convenient shopping centers, Sears bungalows, and Arts & Crafts houses. Property Amenities: ❖ *All Gates Hudson apartment communities work with the Housing Choice Voucher Program* ❖ 24/7 Emergency Maintenance ❖ BBQ Picnic Area ❖ Controlled Access ❖ Convenient Public Transportation ❖ Disability Access ❖ Extra Storage Units ❖ Flexible Rent Payment Options with FLEX ❖ Free On-site parking ❖ Hearing Impaired Accessible ❖ Laundry Facilities in Building ❖ Lobby and Elevator ❖ On-Site Management ❖ Package Acceptance ❖ Pet Play Area ❖ Report Rent and Build Credit with IDIQ ❖ Vision Impaired Accessible Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=hyattsville_house&rp=4341Qttq9Q5A&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=hyattsville_house&rp=4341Qttq9Q5A&t=ap Contact Info: show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Wed: 11:00 AM - 5:30 PM Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Pet Ownership Policy: Cats and Dogs Allowed Max 2 Allowed | One time Fee $250 / Rent $35 Restrictions: Breed and weight restrictions All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 46907727D8714E0D",
