        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Dring's Reach Address: 3407 Robey Ter Silver Spring, MD 20904 Monthly Price: $1772 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 | Baths: 1 | Sq. Footage: 740 sq ft | Terms: 12-Month Contact our leasing office at show contact info + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ✓ Blinds ✓ Cable Available ✓ Carpet ✓ Ceiling Fan(s) ✓ Dining Area ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Disposal ✓ Energy Efficient Appliances ✓ Patio or Balcony ✓ Washer & Dryer in Unit + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ✓ Affordable Housing ✓ Community/Onsite Parking ✓ Fitness Center ✓ On-Line Payments ✓ Online Services ✓ Onsite Maintenance ✓ Onsite Management ✓ Picnic Area ✓ Playground ✓ Central Silver Spring Location ✓ Courtesy Patrol Officer ✓ Parking Included in the Rent ✓ Participates in the Housing Choice Voucher Program ✓ Public Transportation ✓ Shopping, Dining, Entertainment Nearby + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: Don't miss your opportunity to lease a beautiful apartment home at an AMAZING price! The best in moderate income apartment living is right here at Dring's Reach, one of our favorite Silver Spring communities. The beautifully designed one and two bedroom apartments offer breakfast nook with butler counter, cozy fireplace, washer and dryer and formal dining room. There is also an option of a den. The floorplans include a balcony or patio and some have dramatic vaulted ceilings. The community offers a fitness center and outdoor areas. Dring's Reach has a central Silver Spring location with shopping, dining, schools and entertainment all nearby. There is a bus stop at the community entrance and the property is near Rt. 29 and I-95. Pets: Breed Restriction Weight Restriction No Aggressive Breeds. $25 Monthly Pet Rent. $300 Pet Deposit. 45 lbs. Weight Limit. 2 Pet Limit. Contact our leasing office at show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Weekends By Appointment Only. Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=dring's_reach&rp=rzxAhFWxTjaN&t=wb Maximum Income Limits may apply: 50% 1 person - $57,400 or 60% 1 person - $68,880 50% 2 people - $65,600 or 60% 2 person - $78,720 50% 3 people - $73,800 or 60% 3 person - $88,560 50% 4 people - $81,950 or 60% 4 person - $98,340 50% 5 people - $88,550 or 60% 5 person - $106,260 50% 6 people - $95,100 or 60% 6 person - $114,120 50% 7 people - $101,650 or 60% 7 person - $121,980 50% 8 people - $108,200 or 60% 8 person - $129,840 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 671AC1C3C1B347A",
